Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:33.86,注解3,,0,0,0,,禁止将本字幕用于商业用途\N转载请注明 林氏王朝字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当时已经是我到球队后的第二还是第三场主场比赛了\NJeremy lin: So it was like my second or third home game,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至还从未上过场\NAnd I hadn't even been in a game yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当我试图进入球馆时\NAnd I had tried to get in the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拦住我\NAnd they stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说\NAnd they were like,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,“抱歉，这里是球员入口”\N"oh, sorry, this is the players' entrance."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“我知道啊”\NI was like, "I know."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那个保安就困惑地看着我\NHe looked at me confused,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我也困惑地看着他\NAnd then so I was looking at him confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他说\NAnd then he was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“哦，抱歉，你是队上的训练师吗？”\N"oh, I'm sorry. Are you a trainer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我站在那不知道说什么好\NAnd I was just kind of just like standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然后另一个保安走过来\NAnd then another security guard came over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对着之前那个耳语道，“他应该是在队上打球的”\NAnd, like, whispered, "I think he plays on the team."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在上场的是后卫...\NAt guard it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,十七号，林书豪！\NNumber 17, jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪\NHey, jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人认为他会打球\NNobody thought he could play.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要为所得的一切而战\NHe had to fight for everything that he got.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你很少能有这种感觉：你见证了\NIt's not often you think you've seen something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,联盟中罕见的奇迹\NYou couldn't possibly see in the nba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,林投篮！\NLin puts it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,进了！\NBang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，这小子是谁？\NWait a minute. Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，他从哪冒出来的？\NWait. Where's he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，落选秀？\NWait. Not drafted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，被多少球队裁掉过？\NWait. How many teams waived him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当他打球时\NWhen this guy is playing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,勇士队不知道他这么棒\NAnd golden state doesn't know he's any good,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭队不知道他这么棒\NHouston doesn't know he's any good,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不想，难道是因为\NI got to imagine that something has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他看上去不像个打球的好手\NHe doesn't look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪从默默无闻走到伟大\NJeremy lin came from nothing to greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，这小子给所有孩子以希望\NHey, this kid is giving hope to all those kids
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那些认为自己永远不会有机会的孩子\NThat think, "never could I have a chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直对自己说，我的进步历程会是这样\NI always told myself my progression is gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从进入轮换，到成为首发控卫\NBecome a rotation player, become a starting point guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然后赢得NBA总冠军\NAnd then win an nba championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人们听到后肯定会嘲笑我\NAnd people are definitely gonna laugh when they hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有朝一日这一切成真时 \NYou know, they're not gonna be laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就不会再笑了\NIf it actually happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:30.80,注解2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1075,372)}新泽西网队\N\N对\N\N纽约尼克斯\N\N\N2012年2月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:38.30,注解2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,506)}48个小时内，林书豪就会被裁掉\N很可能就此终结他的NBA事业\N并结束他的一生梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,防守！\NDe-fense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,防守！\NDe-fense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队的山姆波特，个人第二次犯规\NNew york foul is on shumpert, his second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他得下场休息会儿了\NAnd now, he'll have to take a seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看看谁要上场了\NAnd, again, mike, look who's coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是林书豪，你可以听到球迷的大声欢呼\NJeremy lin, and you hear a pretty big ovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是神在安排这一切\NJeremy: I know god orchestrated this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太多事情在我的掌控之外\NThere's just too much out of my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且它们发生的方式是那样的不可思议\NAnd just the way it happened is just miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪！\NJeremy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的\N It's actually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在我大概八、九岁后\NAfter, I think, age maybe 8 or 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们换掉了电视\NWe got rid of the tv,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在季后赛时看比赛\NAnd we would just get it during the playoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在家看\NWe would watch it in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在后院\NAnd then, in the backyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有扇玻璃门，外面有个篮筐\NThere's a glass door and a hoop outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在外面透过窗子看\NSo we would just watch through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在场间休息或是暂停时\NAnd then any time there was,like, a break or a time-out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会出去模仿\NWe'd go out, and we'd do the exact move
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚球场上出现过的动作\NThat just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上就全部都是模仿乔丹\NAnd it was pretty much all just copying michael jordan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,并且看到他取得胜利\NAnd watching him win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们热爱那种观看比赛的方式\NAnd so we loved watching basketball that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那一直是我的一个梦想\NAnd it was always a dream of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从未想过它会变成现实\NBut I didn't actually think it would be a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪搞到这个的？\N Where did you get this done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在市中心\N是吗？在格林威治村？\NDown town.\NOh, yeah? Down in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看这个\NCan you take a look? Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看..背上这是..\NLet me see what you... This is the back of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒\NBeautifully done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,无与林比\NLintastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}所有孩子都有自己的梦想\NEvery kid has a dream.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}有些想当消防员，有些想当宇航员\NSome want to be a fireman, others an astronaut.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}大多数时候，梦想只是梦而已\NMost of the time, dreams are just dreams.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这个梦始于加州帕罗奥托\NThis dream starts in palo alto, california,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}旧金山的一片郊区\NA suburb of san francisco,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在这里，一个年轻人学习信仰\NWhere a young man learns about faith,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}坚韧与机遇\NPerseverance, and opportunity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,茄子！\NCheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在台湾，我们只重视学习，我们并不重视打球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:02.45,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,296)}林明杰\N林书豪的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候上完班之后，每次就很累，觉得很累
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想说，我看篮球看了这么多，特别是NBA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就开始练习打篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己练习了五年，像怎么运球，怎么投篮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么上篮，我自己练了五年各式各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我特别喜欢练习的就是贾巴尔的勾手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果有小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们小时候一定要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,带他们一起打篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当爸爸带我们去基督教青年会打球时\NJoshua lin: My dad was taking us to the ymca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在上小学\NWe were still, like, in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,周一、三、五球馆开放\NThere's like open gym Monday,Wednesday, fridays,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.65,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(771,326)}林书雅\N林书豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,从晚上七点半到九点半\NFrom like 7:30 to 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我们放学回家后\NAnd we would just come home from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快做完作业\NAnd we would just all do our homework as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当有人不能完成作业时\NAnd then when someone couldn't finish their assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会互相帮助\NThen we would go and help them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我做不完\NSo if I couldn't finish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥就会来帮我\NJosh would come over and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果弟弟做不完\NIf joe couldn't finish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会去帮他\NYou know, we would go over and help joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们一直学到的一点\NThat's everything we've always known is just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们是兄弟，我们是彼此最好的朋友\NHaving each other and being best friends with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时不喜欢弹钢琴\NI didn't want to play the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我弹得很糟\NAnd I was horrible at the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每年的表演会上\NLike, every year,the recital would come around,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会弹同一首曲子\NAnd I'd be pretty much playing the same song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母就觉得这样不行\NAnd they were just like, "this is not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是在浪费钱\N"I'm wasting my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子只爱打篮球\N"all he does is play basketball,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让他打篮球吧\NSo let's just let him play basketball."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们逐渐爱上这项运动时\NAs we grew to love the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈给予了巨大支持\NMy mom becamea huge supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她能看出我们是真爱篮球\NI think she could just see that we loved basketball,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看出我们心中的热爱与激情\NThat we were passionate about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而她全心爱着我们\NAnd she's passionate about us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以无论我们想做什么\NSo whatever we wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是愿意支持我们\NShe always wanted to support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是开车送大家，她是全队的家长\NShe always drove. She was always a team parent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有二哥和我打过的\NFor every njb, aau
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.60,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(837,324)}林书伟\N林书豪的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全国青少年篮球联赛（NJB）和\N业余体育联盟比赛（AAU）\NThat jeremy played for, that I played for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她总会出现在左右\NShe was always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,支持着我们\NShe was always supporting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是所有的母亲，尤其是亚裔母亲\NYou know, not every mom, asian mom especially,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会支持孩子打篮球\NIs gonna support their child playing basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,坚强的意志\NStrong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,坚强的意志?\NStrong will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,坚强的意志\NStrong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他想要什么东西\NIf he wants something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他会竭尽所能去得到\NHe will do anything to get that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他会把头往地上撞\NSo he will knock his head on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他会故意摔倒\NHe will just make himself fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他会做一切事情来试图得到自己想要的东西\NHe will do anything to get what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在我成长过程中，我的家庭总是强调神是首位的\NGrowing up, my family always emphasized god first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,学业其次，运动第三\NSchool second, athletics third.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始，他们并不确定\NIn the beginning, they weren't sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我能打多久的篮球\NHow long I could play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是决定顺其自然\NThey were just gonna ride it out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,尽可能地享受篮球带来的快乐\NAnd have fun with it as long as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时受邀前往一场\N帕罗奥托的基督教青年会联赛\NJim sutter: I got invited to a y league game in palo alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时就是一个小小孩\NAnd he's just this little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.15,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,410)}吉姆· 萨特\NAAU球队METRO MIRAGE的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想到\NYou know, you wouldn't think it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他的得分能力这么出色\NBut he just scored the basketball so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,第一场比赛时\NThe first tournament we played,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他开始狂投三分\NAnd he just starts just raining 3-pointers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我叫得太大声了\NThey will say I am so loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我会不停喊“防守！”\NBecause I will keep talking, "defense!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或是“抢篮板！”\NYou know, "get a rebound!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,当然他妈妈当时会那样\NOf course, mom's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不停喊“他得了多少分？”\N"how many points\Ndid he score?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她会说，“我告诉过你他棒极了吧”\NShe'd say, "I told you he was pretty good."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会说，“我知道，我知道他很棒”\NI go, "I know. I know he's pretty good."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当时所有AAU的球队都不要书豪\N All the aau team, they never want jeremy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,即便他是当时最棒的控卫\NEven though he's the best point guard at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一支球队\NOnly this particular aau,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Metro Mirage非常想要书豪为他们打球\NMetro mirage, want him so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,耶，书豪！\NYeah, jeremy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢处在这个被轻视的位置\NI love being the underdog
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是我习惯的角色\NJust because it's just what I'm used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我在联盟中会打得不错\NYou know, I would be good in this league,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但人们会说\NAnd then people would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“但是他在这个联盟中不可能打好的”\N"oh, but he can't play well in this league."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,每次书豪对位某个人们都说棒的球员\NEvery time jeremy play against somebody who people say is good,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果书豪打得更好\NIf jeremy played better,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会开始想，其实是这人不行\NThen they start thinking, "that person's not good."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而不会肯定书豪打得好\NThey don't give jeremy credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种十四块钱的超大玉米饼\NThere's a $14 extra-large burrito
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这么大\NThat's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天，你一定得买那个吃\NOh, my gosh, you should totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪，你要买这个大的吗？\NJeremy, you gonna get the big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NJeremy: Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,人与食物大对决\NMan versus food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开启野兽模式了\NI'm about to beast this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道我是怎么长这么高的\NJeremy: I don't know how I got so tall, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我食量很大\NI ate a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去吊单杠\NI would hang\Nfrom monkey bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我会躺在床沿想着\NUm, I would lie off the edge of my bed thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,重力会把我拉长\NThat gravity would pull me and make me taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当我高一时我只有一米六左右\NWhen I was 5'3" as a freshman in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得，我妈妈也记得\NI remember--my mom remembers this, too--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上我钻进车里时\NI would get in the car every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会说，“你们为什么不长高点？”\NAnd I'd be like, "why aren't you taller?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我一直这么矮的原因\NLike, "this is why I'm so short."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈会说，“要怪就怪你爸”\NShe always said, "blame your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“我可不矮”\NI'm not that short."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她有差不多一米六八\NShe's 5'6".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对于亚裔女性来说这挺高的\NFor an asian woman, that's pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸同样是一米六八\NAnd my dad's also 5'6".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.80,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(819,468)}帕罗奥图中学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我对他在篮球上的最大影响\NI think my biggest influence on him as a player,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊得最多的话题\NThe most constant dominant conversation we had
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.85,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,430)}彼得·迪潘布洛克\N帕罗奥图中学1997-2008篮球教练
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是他要为其他队员创造机会\NWas him creating for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高中的时候，他知道他能够在场上\NIn high school, he knew he could get by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好好利用他的天赋\NAnd do well on his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,许多孩子，特别是他\NA lot of kids, and him especially,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一心想着得分\NIt was all about scoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而我跟他聊得最多的\NAnd my constant conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也是他给我的最大难题\NMy constant challenge with him was,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“书豪，你有创造机会的能力\N"jeremy, you're a creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“你真的可以当领头人\N"you could really be the man
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你明白自己是个怎样的球员”\NIf you just embraced who you are as a player."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在他高一那年\NDuring his junior year,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林书豪在学校的维京人队里崭露头角\NJeremy emerged as the vikings' star.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}随着一场场比赛，他的技术和自信渐长\NWith every game, his skills and confidence grew,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但他的自负也随之而长\NBut so did his ego.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一段时间我们甚至打出30胜1负的成绩\NWe were like 30 and 1 at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我们所向披靡\NWe were killing everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始自我膨胀\NI was starting to get a big head,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己很了不起\NThinking I was sweet and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,结果后来我受伤了\NAnd then I get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}高中时林书豪习惯\NJeremy had a tradition of shooting around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在比赛的前一晚练球\NThe night before his high school games.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但是在州半决赛的前一晚\NBut on the eve of the state semifinal game,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}高中的体育馆关门了\NThe high school gym was closed,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林在本地的基督教青年会打了场即兴的比赛\NAnd jeremy played in a pick-up game at his local ymca.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}当晚，林书豪扭伤了脚踝\NThat night, jeremy fractured his ankle,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他的信念将受到考验\NAnd his faith would be tested.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎崩溃了\NI just pretty much broke down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住大哭\NUm, I broke down crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前，我从未经历过严重的打击\NUp until then, like, I'd never gone through any serious tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那次是我当时经历过最糟的事情\NThat was the worst thing that ever happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}由于林书豪无法上场\NWith jeremy on the bench,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}维京人队获得冠军的希望迅速陨灭了\NThe vikings' hopes for a state championship quickly faded.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，对于一个高中生来说\NYou know, from a high schooler's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是非常大的打击\NThat's like everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他退后一步\NI told him to take a step back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用更广阔的视角来看\NAnd to look at it from a bigger perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得我哥哥给我发了一封很长的信\NI remember my brother sent me this really long letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他谈到神如何给予和收回\NHe talks about how god gives and takes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,神拿走了我那时特别在乎的东西\NAnd so god took what I really cared about at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来说明，离开神\NTo show me that I can't do what I want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不能完成我的愿望\NI can't accomplish what I want to accomplish without him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界上，在我的生命里\NAnd that nothing in this world, in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么不是按照神的旨意发生的\NWill happen that's not according to his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当大卫面对巨人歌利亚时\NWhen david faced goliath,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他并不知道结果\NHe didn't know the outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但他对神有热忱\NBut he was zealous for the living god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道书豪把神放在第一位\NWith jeremy, I know he puts the order, god first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其次是家人，第三是篮球\NFamily second, basketball third.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:43.00,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,358)}史提芬·陈\N林书豪的牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他会告诉你\NAnd he'll tell you this now at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,回顾过去，神主宰着这一切\NLooking back, it's more of, god is in all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,高中时，他很谦虚\NAnd in high school, he was humbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道不能以一己之力完成所有事情\NHe learned that he couldn't do everything himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门\NAmen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他只能信赖神\NAnd he could only put his faith in god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉自己\NI told myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我只剩一年确定可以打篮球了\NI have one year left of guaranteed basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我要全力以赴\NI said I'm gonna do everything I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我将力拼到底\NAnd I'm gonna go out fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确保我们还会回到这里\NAnd I'm gonna make sure that we get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他的镇定是一个高四学生少有的\NHe had unusual poise for a high school senior,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,特别地自信\NUnusual confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上有某种东西让我明白\NThere was something about him that I could see
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:28.05,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,268)}米驰·史提芬\N国内专栏作家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他在球场上是个好领袖\NWhy he was a great leader on the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会不自觉被他吸引\N'cause you're just driven to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你能感觉到他的心跳\NYou can feel his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每次他们比分很接近的时候\NEvery close game they had,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪就会有关键的表现\NJeremy lin was making a big play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每次的方式都不一样\NAnd it was every different way--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛最后关头的三分，或者抢断\NA 3-pointer, a steal at the end of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但每次都有他的参与\NBut every one, he was in the middle of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是那个挺身而出的人\NHe was the guy doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,林从右侧跳投\NLin takes a jump shot right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,中了！\NHits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的跳投\NOh, a nice jump shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,林的三分，有了！\NLin for 3. Buries it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}没有什么能够阻止林书豪\NNothing was going to stop jeremy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}把他的球队带回到州决赛\NFrom getting his team back to the state championship,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}很快，帕罗奥图中学面对着自己的巨人歌利亚\NAnd, soon enough, palo alto faced goliath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在阿科球馆里的对阵双方\N是马特蒂中学和帕罗奥图中学\NAnnouncer: Inside arco arena, it's mater dei and palo alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是加州校际联盟第二分区的州冠军决赛\NIt's the cif division ii state championship
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,预告之后马上开始\NJust moments away from tip-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想很多人都认为\NI think a lot of people just assumed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能来到州冠军决赛\NThat getting to the state championship game,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帕罗奥图中学已经满足了\NPalo alto would be satisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪已经满足了\NJeremy lin would be satisfied with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和马特蒂中学的比赛\NAnd it was just much more of a formality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是走个形式罢了\NWhen they played mater dei high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,南加州的学校排名都很靠前\NSouthern california schools dominate the rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都是强队\NThey're the powers that be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在郊区的帕罗奥图中学，不怎么样\NPalo alto, out in the suburbs, not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都说，马特蒂中学肯定赢\NEverybody said mater dei was the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,马特蒂中学优势很大\NMater dei is the big dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,马特蒂中学在全国排名11位\NMater dei, number 11 in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,赛前的一整个星期\NThe whole week leading up to the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我都在想，我们怎么才能抢到篮板？\NIt was just like, "how we gonna get a rebound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么才能打好？\NHow we gonna be able to play?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得在校园里走时\NI remember walking around campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很多记者跑来问\NAnd there are all these reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你们能赢？\NAnd they'd be like, "oh, you think you can win?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要怎么打赢他们？\NLike, "how you gonna beat 'em?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人，包括我的朋友都问我\NAnd everyone's asking me, my friends were asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,后来当他们问“你觉得你们能打赢他们？”\NBy the end, they're like, "you think you can beat 'em?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说：“来看比赛就知道了。”\NI was like, "man, just come to the game and watch."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}马特蒂中学不仅有\NAlong with mater dei's{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}引以为傲的历史和强大的名气\NDecorated history and dominant reputation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这支校队还有8名身高1.98米以上的球员\NThis varsity team had 8 players over 6'6".{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到对手是帕罗奥图时，还松了口气\NI was kindof relieved that we were playing palo alto,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.80,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(851,352)}格瑞·麦克奈\N马特蒂高中篮球教练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但我越看他们的录像，越感觉到\NBut the more I watched them on tape, I just had a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你还别说\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这些小伙子比我想象的要厉害\NThese guys are better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没两下子，是不可能打到州决赛的\NYou know, you don't get to the state finals by not being good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,林的球\NHere's lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来个好球吧，他做到了\NNeeds something good, and he finally got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,教练：我们一点都没被镇住\NDiepenbrock: We were not intimidated at all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的全力以赴打好比赛\NAnd really came out playing our game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,林的球，这就是他们说的\NHere's lin. Oh, there's that quick first step
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很快的第一步\NThat they talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,帕罗奥图打了一波9比2，到此为止\NPalo alto on a 9-2 run, and that's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子三分厉害\NThat kid can throw the triple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从纸面上所有人都会说无论从体格、\NEverybody on paper would say the size,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,运动能力还是速度，帝王队（对手球队名）都更强\NThe athleticism, the quickness is with the monarchs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但从斗志来说，维京人队更胜一筹\NBut it's the heart that is with the vikings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚他们的斗志得到充分的体现\NAnd their heart has been on display so far tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛的最后\NMcknight: At the end of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在关键的时刻投进了重要的球\NHe hit the big shots at the big moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,林的球\NHere's lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有投中距离，直接攻击篮筐！\NWithout that 7-footer, he can go to the rack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当比赛悬于一线时，他接管了比赛\NWhen the game was on the line, yeah, he took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,进攻时间只剩4秒了\NFour seconds on the shot clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,林不得不远距离投篮\NAnd lin is gonna have to launch a 25-footer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,中了！\NOh, it went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有意安排的吗？我看不像\NDid he call that? I think he called that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是自然发生的\NIt happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人期望他们能战胜帝王队\NNo one gave them a prayer to be on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们没有帝王队所拥有的\NWith the athletes and the thoroughbreds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,精心培养的运动人才\NThat the monarchs have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到达最高点，这是最棒的感觉\NIt's the best feeling to go out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是美梦成真\NI mean, it is a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我喜欢高中篮球\NIt's why we love high school basketball
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这样的笑脸\NBecause of faces like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,教练：当我纵观这一切\NDiepenbrock: When I really looked at everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一个篮球运动员\NEverything a basketball player
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,能够为他自己\NCould do for himself individually
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为球队做的一切\NAnd for a team,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪都是这里最好的球员\NJeremy lin was the best player here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可是大学并没有争着要他\NBut yet colleges weren't clamoring for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他不符合固有的模式\NHe just didn't fit the mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,高中毕业时\NAfter my senior year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常想在大学打篮球\NI was just dying to play in college,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且觉得自己有这个实力\NAnd I felt like I deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:15.20,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1007,462)}15.4分\N6.2助攻\N4.2抢断\N北加州第二分区\N年度最佳球员\N\N全加州第一阵容球员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那个过程很长\NI remember it was just a very long process,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很沮丧，因为我问了一间又一间的\NVery frustrating,because I was going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太平洋十校联盟的院校\NFrom pac 10 school to pac 10 school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.32,注解1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675,370)}太平洋十校联盟：是一个美国西部的大学体育联盟，\N成员包括斯坦福大学等名校，现已改名为太平洋十二校联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至得不到\NI couldn't even get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,第三分区的学校青睐\NSome division iii schools to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而我特别想去斯坦福大学\NAnd I was dying to go to stanford.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我常常去他们学校打球\NUm, I would go there and play with them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我会问他们的教练\NI would always ask their coach, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎样才能到你队里打球？\N"what can I do to play for you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我常说如果我是黑人\NYeah, I've always said, if I was black,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会得到第一分区学校的奖学金\NI would have gotten a d-1 scholarship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但那只是我的个人意见\NBut that's my personal opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,教练：他是个亚裔孩子\NDiepenbrock: Well, he's an asian kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有两米身高的亚裔孩子\NHe's an asian kid, and he's not 7-foot tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你很少见到亚裔的控卫\NAnd you don't see a lot of asian point guards
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能进入第一分区的篮球队\NMaking it in division I basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想法很简单，但那就是他们的想法\NSuch a simple kind of thought, but that was the thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,, 我会说，他和我有共鸣\NI say...I say he's relatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.00,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,390)}范振书亚\N林书豪的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我见过最脚踏实地的人之一\NHe's one of the most down-to-earth guys I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是开玩笑\NWe're always joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总是互相搞恶作剧\NWe're always, you know, pranking on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那些蓝色的点缀吗？\NUm, did you see the blue accented stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到啊，你喜欢那种蓝色？\N I did see it. You like that blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我很喜欢那种蓝色\NYeah. I really like that blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我走进来时\N'cause when I walk in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要只有黑和白\NI don't want it to be like black, white, black.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要大家都惊叹\NI want people to be like, "dang."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，这个\NOh, shoot, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的墙壁需要不同的点缀\NDifferent walls need different accents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是清仓甩卖的\NThese are clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，看这个\NYeah, dang, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看，才10美元\NLook at this. 10 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人们跟他一起的时候\NI think when people hang out with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会发现\NThey just realize he's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是个普通人\NYou know, he's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听着不错，好，再见\NSounds good. All right, see you later, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}虽然被评为年度最佳球员\NDespite being named player of the year{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}还获得了加州冠军\NAnd winning a state championship,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林书豪得到的唯一一份\NJeremy's only offer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}能够打篮球的大学录取通知\NTo play basketball on the collegiate level{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是一所“小”学校\NWas from a small university{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哈佛\NCalled harvard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天上课\NMy first day at class,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我被彻底吓着了\NI was just super-intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我去参加数学分班测验\NI went and took my math placement test,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说，如果你不会做\NAnd they were like, "if you don't know how to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以交卷走人\NFeel free to turn it in and leave."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着试卷，心想\NI looked at it and I was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐，我啥也看不懂\N"dude, I don't know what's going on here."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我交了卷\NSo I turned it in, and I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概是第二个交卷的\NLike, maybe the second person who turned it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我心想，天，我在哈佛的\NI was like, "man, I just, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,第一场测验就挂了\NFailed my first test at harvard."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天，我们进行中文分班测验\NThe next day, we had the chinese placement test,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们说\NAnd they gave us the test, and they're like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你读不懂，可以交卷\N"if you can't read it, just turn it in."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我读不懂啊，就又交卷了\NI couldn't read it, so I turned it in again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是连续两次测验挂掉\NAnd that was back-to-back failed tests
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至一个答案都写不出\NWithout even filling in an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我在电话里跟我妈妈说\NI called my mom, I was like, "man,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以后估计很难熬了，要做好心理准备\NThis is gonna be pretty tough, so just get ready."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很大程度上，林书豪去哈佛\NIn a lot of ways, jeremy lin going to harvard
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是符合逻辑的\NWas a very logical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛有23名\NThere were 23 asian-americans at harvard
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,姓林的亚裔学生\NWhose last name was lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以林进入哈佛\NAnd so for jeremy lin to show up at harvard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,作为亚裔的孩子\NBeing this asian-american kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,数学成绩好\NWho had a perfect math sat ii score was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道，并不少见\NYou know, nothing rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他打篮球很厉害的这个事实（却很特别）\NBut the fact that he was amazing at this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是他如何融入哈佛？\NThe question was then how did he fit in at harvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米·艾默科\NThere is tommy amaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,1987年毕业于杜克大学（篮球名校）\N1987 graduate of duke, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在哈佛的第一年\NFirst year at harvard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有11年的主教练经验\N11th year overall as a head coach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,180场胜利\N180 career wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}随着前密歇根大学的教练汤米·艾默科的到来\NWith the hiring of former michigan coach tommy amaker,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哈佛决心走进\NHarvard was committed to a new era{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}篮球上的新时代\NIn their basketball program.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}艾默科在杜克大学是明星球员\NAmaker was a star player at duke university,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}后来当了九年的助教\NThen spent nine years as an assistant coach{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}辅佐传奇教练迈克·沙舍夫斯基（老K教练）\NTo the legendary mike krzyzewski.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哈佛的篮球版图\NThe basketball landscape at harvard{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}正准备改头换面\NWas about to be transformed,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}而林书豪是排头兵\NAnd jeremy was leading the charge.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们有些特别的因素\NWe knew we had something pretty interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是林书豪\NEspecially with jeremy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为首先他训练特别刻苦\NBecause of how hard he worked, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,而且篮球对他而言非常重要\NAnd how important basketball was to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有就是他的天赋\NAnd then his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他被大大地低估了\NI think he was very much underrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.28,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他想按照\NAnd I think he wanted to play in the style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们推行的\NAnd the system, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,风格和系统打球\NThat we weregonna implement,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是高能量的风格\NWhich is gonna be high octane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他的球风很强硬\NAnd he's a hard-charging,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,侵略性强，无所畏惧\NAggressive, fearless player.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪断球\NA steal by jeremy lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,轻松扣篮\NHe's gonna go in for the easy jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头看\NLooking up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,林撕裂了防守并成功上篮！\NLin splits defenders and lays it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我做教练15年\NIn my 15 years of coaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在杜克大学打了4年球\NMy four years at duke,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过任何人\NI've never seen anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像林书豪那么努力\NWork as diligent and as hard as jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他每天都来，认真训练\NHe came in every day and put the work in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每天看录像\NWe watched film every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:04.78,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,410)}肯尼·布雷肯尼\N哈佛大学2007-2011男篮助教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们训练前后也在练习\NWe did work before and after practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常勤奋\NHe busted his tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要求他做的，他都做到了\NAnd he did all the things that we asked him to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,弧顶出手，大三分，林书豪！\NTop of the circle, deep 3, jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎比赛场面越大，他打得越好\NIt seems the bigger the game, the better he played.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场大东部的篮球赛\NIt's big east basketball,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,排名第13的康涅狄格大学哈士奇队\N对阵哈佛大学的猩红队\NAs the 13th ranked uconn huskies host the crimson of harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.26,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要注意的是林书豪\NNow, keep an eye on jeremy lin today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的球员\NThis is the type of player
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能够只手帮助猩红队\NThat can single-handedly help the crimson
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,起死回生\NPull off a miraculous upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,艾默科：他是场上最棒的球员\NAmaker: He was the best player on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那说明了很多事情\NYou know, that's saying a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当你面对的是\NWhen you're speaking of a team
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,像康涅狄格大学这样的球队时\Nthat was the caliber of connecticut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,多漂亮的篮底动作\NWhat a move on the runner off the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想那时候大家都认为\NI think that's when everybody was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他不只是一个好的大学球员这么简单\N"all right, he's more than just, like, a good college player.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:45.90,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,404)}奥利佛·麦克纳里\N后卫，哈佛大学篮球队2008-2012
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他让一支很厉害的球队颜面尽失\NLike, he just made a very good team look bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,凯西球被打出去，戴森抢断\NCasey had it knocked away,and a steal by dyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,林跟到篮下\NTakes lin to the basket,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,林在篮边给他一个盖帽！\NAnd lin blocks him at the rim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的盖帽\NWhat a block.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,艾默科：他拿了30分\NAmaker: Scoring 30 points there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在各方面都有贡献\NBeing a force to deal with in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:23:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,回到林手上，来到禁区，假动作，切到篮下\NBack to lin top of the key, pump fake, drives
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,双手扣进！\NAnd throws it down with both hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪的漂亮扣篮！\NOh, what a dunk by jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们一直相信\NHe kept us believing all the way through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有机会\NThat we have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这小子在各个方面都领导者这支球队\NThis guy's leading this team in every category, not just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.30,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,386)}丹·达根\N体育作者，波士顿先驱报
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他不只是个得分手\NI mean, it wasn't like he was just a scorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是最好的防守队员\NHe was the best defensive player,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抢篮板最好，传球最好\NHe was the best rebounder, the best passer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他基本上什么都最好\NYou know, he pretty much could do it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在那些时刻\NIt was just kind of like those moments
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,关键的时刻或者决定胜负的时刻\NWhere it was crunch time and winning time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会站出来？\NYou know, who's gonna step up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,回到另一边，给到葛迪\NBack the other way, comes to gurdy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,进入前场\NInto the frontcourt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,切入到右侧\NDrives down the right lane line,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,右手上篮！中了！\NGoes up with the right hand! Lays it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩三秒！哈佛回到另一边！\NThree seconds left! Harvard back the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,落后一分，林书豪！\NDown by a point, jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,中场被撞倒！\NBumped at midcourt!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.97,0:24:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他被犯规，但还是投进了！\NHe's fouled, but got it to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛赢了！哈佛赢了！\NHarvard wins it! Harvard wins it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信！\NUnbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪投进了难以置信的一球\NJeremy lin on an unbelievable shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.05,0:24:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛赢了！\NAnd harvard has won
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以最不可思议的方式！\NIn the most improbable fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.35,0:24:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信！\NI don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.46,0:24:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候\NWhen I was growing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.29,0:25:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,参加AAU的比赛\NI was playing in the aau tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.06,0:25:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比赛的时候\NWe would play in games,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候，人们会说\NAnd a couple of times, people would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“哟，滚回到中国去”\N"yo, take your ass back to china,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说：“你就是个中国货”之类的\NOr like, "you're a chinese import," or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.44,0:25:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,上了大学以后，这些攻击更离谱了\NWhen I got to college, it just, like, got crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说：“中国佬！”\NIt was just like, "you chink!"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.64,0:25:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么“你能张开眼睛吗？”\NYou know, "can you even open your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.34,0:25:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得见分数牌吗？\NCan you see the scoreboard?"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这种乱七八糟的东西\NYou know, just like crazy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我心想：这都什么跟什么啊？\NAnd I'd just be like, "dude, like, what is going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.21,0:25:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}身处目光的焦点中\NBeing in the spotlight{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.58,0:25:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}为林书豪带来不可避免的副产物\NBrought jeremy an inevitable byproduct:{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.55,0:25:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}关注，有正面的，也有负面的\NAttention, both positive and negative.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,人们在看篮球运动员时\NI mean, people look at basketball players in terms of...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果用种族的角度去看\NOf race a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在美国，篮球往往被视为\NBasketball is not considered
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.03,0:25:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不是给亚裔玩的运动\NAn asian sport here in america.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.27,0:25:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打客场时\NWe'd be playing on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在常春藤的某个体育馆里\NSpecific gyms in the ivy league,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.90,0:25:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会向他喊一些种族歧视的脏话\NAnd they would yell racial slurs to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在常春藤联盟，看到种族歧视的辱骂\NIt was shocking to me to see racial taunts
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.21,0:25:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让我很惊讶\NIn the ivy league,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到了这个级别\NBecause you think that at that level,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当然你会认为\NCertainly in the supposed, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.81,0:25:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,学术氛围应该很浓厚\NVery academically progressively oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:26:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些校园里会有很多亚裔的学生\NGroup of schools full of asian students on their campuses
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,种族歧视的侮辱应该是不可想象的\NThat that would be something that was unthinkable,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.42,0:26:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实并非如此\NBut it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他，这是一种重视的表现\NI just told him, it's a sign of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是，他们很无知\NYeah, they're ignorant,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.30,0:26:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但说到底\NBut at the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.63,0:26:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们想要进入你的脑子\NThey're trying to get in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想着他们说的东西\NYou're thinking about what they saying
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.14,0:26:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而没有想着比赛\NAnd not thinking about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是在训练中\NI think we were just working out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.01,0:26:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他说\NAnd kind of was like, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.75,0:26:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪，能跟你说句话吗？\N"j, can I speak to you for a moment?"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.95,0:26:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我坐下\NHe sat me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.35,0:26:37.95,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(935,450)}4.4 助攻/场\N4.4 篮板/场\N16.4 分/场\N\N\N总共 1,483 分
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.22,0:26:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在体育馆外的楼梯上\NLike, right outside the gym on the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.06,0:26:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他说\NAnd he was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.69,0:26:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道有没有人告诉过你\N"I don't know if anybody's ever told you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.49,0:26:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得你可以去打NBA\NBut I think you can be an nba player."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他看着我的表情\NAnd he kind of looked at me like, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.60,0:26:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就像看到圣诞老人\NHe just saw santa claus or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.87,0:26:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，你疯了吧\NYou know, I was just like, "you're crazy," you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.94,0:26:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，兄弟，你肯定疯了\NI was like, "dude, you are crazy."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.40,0:26:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈会说\NMy mom, you know, would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去打NBA\N"you can make it to the nba."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.08,0:26:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，好吧……妈\N"all right. Um, okay, mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.11,0:27:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能吗？\NIs this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许他真的\NI thought maybe he really...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有这个可能\NReally have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.42,0:27:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当这个问题被提起\NWhen the question was broached,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.99,0:27:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪是不是有能力进入NBA\NIs jeremy lin good enough to make the nba,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.16,0:27:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想正是从那时开始他对这件事情产生兴趣\NThat's when I think a lot of the interest started surging.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.56,0:27:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我这张毯子的来历吗？\NCan you tell me the history of this blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这张毯子来头可大了\NOh, this blanket is legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.30,0:27:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.50,0:27:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,上面全是《狮子王》的角色\NIt's all about {\i1}lion king.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.94,0:27:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有娜娜\NWe have nala right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.30,0:27:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有小辛巴，丁满和彭彭\NBaby simba, timon and pumbaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.87,0:27:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我一直以来最喜欢的毯子\NThis is one of my favorite blankets of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.24,0:27:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,芝麻街那条毯子呢？\NWhat about the {\i1}sesame street blanket?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.24,0:27:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我第二喜欢的是那条加菲猫的\NNo. My second favorite is the garfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.31,0:27:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后才到芝麻街那条\NAnd then {\i1}sesame street.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.58,0:27:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天……好吧，球迷们\Noh, man. All right, fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.88,0:27:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好，欢迎来到2010年度选秀\NGood evening, and welcome to the 2010 draft
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.69,0:27:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来到纽约的麦迪逊花园\NAt madison square garden in new york city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.79,0:27:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一轮，我们也没抱什么期望\NThe first round, we weren't expecting really much of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚意味着\NTonight marks the realization of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最好的年轻球员梦想成真\NFor the best young players in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.47,0:27:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都很紧张\NWe were just all real nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.20,0:27:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他需要克服很多障碍\NJust 'cause there were so many odds to overcome for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:28:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,状元签，华盛顿巫师队(奇才队)\NAnd with the first pick, the washington wizards
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.01,0:28:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,选择来自肯塔基大学的约翰·沃尔\NSelect john wall from the university of kentucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.28,0:28:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实满怀着希望，但是说实在话\NI was hopeful,but to be completely honest
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.05,0:28:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,心里真正想的是：拭目以待到底会发生什么吧\NI was like, "let's just wait and see what happens."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.02,0:28:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直留意着种族问题\NThe thing that I'm always interested in is race
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.99,0:28:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,联盟里种族歧视这种风气一直存在\NAnd the way discrimination,you know, rears its ugly head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.76,0:28:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇是否有球队会尝试冒险\NI was really interested in seeing if a team would take the plunge
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.63,0:28:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去选一个美籍亚裔球员\NAnd take this asian-american player.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.13,0:28:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思的是\NYou know, it was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.63,0:28:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我最有机会选上的球队\NLike, the team that I had the highest chance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是尼克斯\NTo get drafted b was the knicks,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.67,0:28:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我在试训里打得特别好\Ncause I crushed that workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.34,0:28:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,2010 NBA选秀大会第39顺位是\NWith the 39th pick in the 2010 nba draft...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.05,0:28:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想“如果在这里我没有被选中” \NI was like,"if I don'get drafted here
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.55,0:28:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我很有可能就不会被任何球队选了\NI probably won't get drafted."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.15,0:28:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约尼克斯队的选择是\NThe new york knicks select...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.92,0:28:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想“天啊，如果我被选中了我该做些什么？”\NI'm thinking like,"oh, if I get drafted，what's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该要围着会场跑一圈，拥抱每个人吗？\NI'm just gonna run around, like，hugging everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.76,0:28:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我就要飞去纽约了\NI'm gonna fly to new york tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.09,0:28:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德里·菲尔兹，来自斯坦福大学\NLandry fields，from stanford university.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.47,0:29:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}选秀结束后十分钟\N10 minutes{\i}after the draft ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.84,0:29:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}达拉斯小牛队的经理唐尼.尼尔森\NDonny nelson,{\i\i1}the general manager{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.64,0:29:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}亲自打电话给林书豪\NOf the dallas mavericks,{\i\i1}personally called jeremy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.27,0:29:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}让他为小牛队夏季联赛效力\NAnd asked him to play{\i\i1}on his summer league team.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.44,0:29:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想大概每个落选的人\NI think everyone who goes undrafted,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.51,0:29:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都会有一种想要证明自己的心情，因为他们觉得自己有实力\NFeels like they have to prove themselves,because they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.48,0:29:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，这对我而言确实是一个好机会\NAnd so, you know,this is a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.92,0:29:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在夏季联赛的赛场\NWhere you get to play against people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.49,0:29:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,每晚跟选秀大会上落选的球员们一起打球\NWho are drafted every single night
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.39,0:29:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在实战中与他们竞争\NAnd you get to compete with them in practice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.96,0:29:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而这恰好就是最好的机会\NAnd this is the best opportunity to, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.13,0:29:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,证明给所有的球队看\NProve to all the other teams
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.43,0:29:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是值得被选中的\NThat you deserved to be drafted
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.90,0:29:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来应该得到一份合同\NAnd you deserved to have that contract
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.97,0:29:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，巧妙的进攻\NLin, surprise attack
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.70,0:29:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是一场很有看头的比赛\NOh, this is gonna be interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德斯在防守，林成功保住这一球！\NSanders there，lin protected it home!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.97,0:29:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！漂亮的进球\NWow! Nice play.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.61,0:29:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望林书豪能成功\NI hoped that jeremy would make it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.38,0:29:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我对他的实力有信心\NBecause I had confidence in his ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我疑虑的是\NBut I was skeptical
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.65,0:29:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有一处可以让他真正一展身手的地方\NIn terms of him getting a real shot anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.32,0:29:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪！\NJeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.32,0:29:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,接着在夏季联赛\NAnd then I watched him play
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.02,0:29:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了他与沃尔的对决\NIn the summer league against john wall
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.96,0:29:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将看到非常精彩的对位\NI think we got a primetime match-up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.79,0:30:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·沃尔，联盟选秀的状元\NJohn wall, the number one overall selection
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.30,0:30:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔进攻！反手上篮！\NWall, creative!On the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.30,0:30:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,速度够快吧？\NHow fast was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.90,0:30:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在比赛前一天我告诉林书豪\NI talked to him the day before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.60,0:30:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他将跟约翰·沃尔对位\NHe was gonna play against john wall
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.37,0:30:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你关键的一次表现机会\NAnd I told him,"it's your one shot
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.98,0:30:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟沃尔对位你完全没有问题\NThere's no doubt that you can play against the guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，单手上篮！\NLin.Lin gettin' up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.05,0:30:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,林将成为联盟里的新宠\NHe's gonna be an nba crowd favorite
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.35,0:30:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在进攻端再次得手\NGotta work on the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.82,0:30:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,林在右路绕过防守，在他习惯的右路上篮 \NLin went right around him on his strong side
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.76,0:30:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪具有\NThe fact that he could do that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.79,0:30:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,与新秀状元对位的能力，这个事实令人激动\NAgainst the number-one player in the nba draft was tremendous
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,评估，建设性的意见\NAssessing,constructive criticism
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.57,0:30:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好球！\N No way. Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.60,0:30:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你激发出他的能力，你会看到意想不到的事情\NIf you explode on him,you'll have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.91,0:30:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你会看到他身上蕴藏着无限的可能\NYou're gonna get your opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.91,0:30:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他撕开防守，转身投篮\NAs he splits,spins...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.34,0:30:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太可惜了！裁判为什么要吹哨子？！\NOh, no, ref!Don't you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.58,0:30:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,观众们都站起来了！\NThey're on their feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀，这恐怕是要引起一场混战啊\NOh, my god.This is about to be a melee here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:30:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拉开他们（解说员开玩笑）\NHold 'em back,hold 'em back!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快看，观众们已经陷入疯狂了\NOh, look it, the crowd is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.66,0:31:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他改变了一些人的狭隘眼光\NHe's opened some eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.99,0:31:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果林不再留在小牛为夏季联赛效力\NAnd if lin doesn't stick with the mavs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.06,0:31:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,会有球队看着他的表现，心想\NThere are teams out there that are looking at him saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.26,0:31:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐，他完全推翻了我们的观念\N "boy, he beats their system very nicely."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.06,0:31:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,\N不管他今年是否留在夏季联赛\NWhether he's in the league this year or not
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都会有几支球队想要他的\NHe'll have some options
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.37,0:31:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，会有几支球队想要他的\NOh, he will have some options.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.70,0:31:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一心想要打球\NI'm just trying to play
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.50,0:31:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有球队有兴趣与我谈\NAnd if someone's interested, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.01,0:31:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常乐意去争取机会\NI'd love to talk about an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.14,0:31:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子跟林书豪都是组织后卫\NJoe lacob: My son and he both were point guards
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在AAU分属不同的球队\NAnd they were on different aau teams
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:32.30,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,368)}乔·拉可布\N金州勇士队老板
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.35,0:31:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,记得在当地的体育馆\NAnd so I remember watching them play
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.05,0:31:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过他们的AAU比赛\NThese aau games in these local gyms.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我跟我的合伙人正好买下了勇士队\NBut I just happened to buy the team at that time with my partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.69,0:31:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最早跟总经理说的其中一件事就是\NOne of the first things I told our gm was,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.23,0:31:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“我知道那个球员，我的儿子也知道他”\N"look, I know this kid.My son knows this kid.”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.03,0:31:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常有天赋，我们应该给他一个机会“\NHe's really talented.We ought to give him a shot."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.70,0:31:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们都觉得我有点疯了\NI think they thought we were a little crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.63,0:31:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们还是那么做了，当你是老板\NBut we did, and, you know,when you're the owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.27,0:31:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你就有权利做些疯狂的事\NYou get to do things like that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,勇士队球员的平均智商以及篮球智商\NThe warriors' iq and basketball iq
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.98,0:31:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都上升了一些\NJust went up a few points
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.31,0:31:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们签了哈佛毕业的后卫林书豪\NThey signed harvard guard jeremy lin
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我打给林书豪告诉他我们将签下他\NI called jeremy to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.78,0:32:03.80,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(837,388)}罗杰·蒙哥马利\N林书豪的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.78,0:32:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至不相信这是真的\NHe didn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他说“别开玩笑了，你是认真的吗？”\NHe was like,"stop playing, man.Are you serious?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.65,0:32:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我说“小伙子，这是真的”\NI said,"man, it's for real
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.85,0:32:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,“明天就来场地练习”\N"go down to the practice facility tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.59,0:32:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“然后签下合同，很好吧”\NAnd sign the contract.It's good."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.89,0:32:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他说“老兄，我待会给你回电！”\NAnd he was like,"man! I'll call you back."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.60,0:32:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我几乎不敢相信“天啊”\NI was like, "aah!"you know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.80,0:32:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫醒我弟弟\NI picked my little brother up,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.53,0:32:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说：金州勇士队签我了\NI'm like, "I'm signing with golden state!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.67,0:32:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我又跑到另一个房间 \NAnd I ran into the next room,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,叫醒我哥哥\NI picked my other brother up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.71,0:32:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“勇士队要跟我签约了！”\N"I'm signing with golden state!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.44,0:32:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很难描述是怎样一种心情\NI can't even really describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.51,0:32:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们兄弟从小就为NBA着迷\Ncause we, like, grew up,like, fantasizing about the nba
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.91,0:32:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从小到大都支持着勇士队\NAnd, like, the fact that we grew up rooting for the warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切使书豪进入勇士队显得更不可思议\NMade it even that much crazier
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,作为当代的第一位美籍亚裔NBA球员\NLin has a chance to make history
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.89,0:32:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪很有机会创造历史\NAs the first asian-americannba player in the modern era
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.06,0:32:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当他被勇士选中\NWhen he got picked up by warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.19,0:32:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时刻我们想\NThat moment,we think
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.60,0:32:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“这就是我希望他做的事情”\N"this is what I want him to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.53,0:32:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的梦想就是在NBA打球\NMy dream was to play in the nba,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.97,0:32:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我即将在勇士队完成我的梦想 \NAnd now I get to do it for the warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.47,0:32:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是看着这支球队的比赛长大的\NThe team that I grew up watching
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.90,0:33:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以加入勇士队的意义比梦想成真还要深远\NIt's more than a dream come true
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.48,0:33:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道观众为什么欢呼，林书豪上场了\NWe know what that's about
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.31,0:33:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，曾是帕罗奥多高中的学生\NJeremy lin.Palo alto high school's own
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.98,0:33:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业于哈佛的勇士新秀\NWarrior rookie out of harvard
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.85,0:33:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我上场的时候球馆欢呼声很大\NIt got pretty loud
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.22,0:33:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,观众们站起来为我鼓掌\NAnd people were standing up and clapping
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.96,0:33:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我环顾四周\NAnd I just remember looking around
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.53,0:33:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,\N从小是勇士队的球迷\NGrew up a warrior fan
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.96,0:33:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,长大后被他家乡的球队签下\NSigned by his hometown team
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.73,0:33:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个了不起的故事\NIt's a great story
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此 \NIt really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.40,0:33:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于来到勇士队，我终于成为勇士队的一员\NIt was so emotional for me to finally get there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.94,0:33:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的让我感慨良多\NFor me to finally be there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.60,0:33:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一年前我真的不敢想象我会出现在那里\NAnd I couldn't envision myself there even a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.04,0:33:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看着他防守科比，我的感觉真的是（难以言喻）“哇~”\NWhen I saw him guarding kobe,I was like, "wow."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.05,0:33:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从小就看科比比赛\NWe've been watching this guy ever since we were little
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.82,0:33:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在……居然可以和科比同时在场上\NHe's actually...He's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.09,0:33:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没进，大卫李拿下篮板球\NMissing,lee with the rebound.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.03,0:33:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢看林控球，不要犯规阻碍他\NI love what lin did.Didn't foul him
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.19,0:33:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~！\NOhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.76,0:33:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,准备给灰熊还一记颜色\NReady to returnfor the grizzlies.Williams
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.63,0:34:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,林有一个空档\NLin's got an open look
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.27,0:34:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,结果莫名其妙把球传给了巴蒂尔\NAnd then threw it to battier inexplicably
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.34,0:34:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到NBA\NWelcome to the nba
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.81,0:34:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌所有人都盯着我看\NI hate when everyone's looking at me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.05,0:34:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌聚光灯 \NI hate the spotlight
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.01,0:34:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我如何保持心态做我自己\NHow am I gonna be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.68,0:34:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,每当我碰到球\NWhen every time I touch the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.05,0:34:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都期待着我有疯狂的表现\NEveryone's expecting me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.58,0:34:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,期待我带来不可思议的比赛\NSome crazy, miraculous play?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.22,0:34:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他得分了！\NHe scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.75,0:34:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,观众们可以从我的表情看出一些端倪\NPeople could see it on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.95,0:34:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,譬如我在场上打球\N Like, I was out there playing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.42,0:34:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我并没有打出自己风格\NBut I wasn't playing my brand of basketball
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.89,0:34:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得焦虑不安\NI was scared, nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.63,0:34:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,心里有很多的疑惑\NAnd just, like,a lot of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.99,0:34:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的压力\NAnd a lot of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.23,0:34:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉周围有很多的不确定因素扰乱在心间\NAnd a lot of uncertainty floating around
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.30,0:34:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他缺少那么点运气\NThe ingredient that's missing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.75,0:34:39.40,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(935,400)}拉里·莱利\N金州勇士队\N2009-2012年总经理
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,球队里已经有两个排在他前面的后卫了\NIs the fact there was a player named monta ellis
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.80,0:34:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蒙塔埃利斯和库里\NAnd steph curry ahead of him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.51,0:34:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在NBA水准的比赛里，教练们无疑都想赢球\NYou know, coaches need to win,at the nba level
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.24,0:34:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我们队的教练基思·斯玛特\NAnd so keith smart, who was our coach at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.78,0:34:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,确实没怎么让他上场\N Really didn't play him a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.22,0:34:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样\NAnd this is how these things happen
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.08,0:34:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始我告诉自己\NAt first, I was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.52,0:34:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“他知道我有实力，他知道我可以上场比赛”   \N"he knows I can play,he knows I can play."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.99,0:34:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是事实是我基本上没有机会上场 \NAnd then I wasn't playing at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.49,0:34:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我看到体育新闻里写\N And then I was, like,reading all these articles like,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.06,0:34:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“看吧，把他签进来只是为了多卖几件球衣”\N"oh, he's just here to sell jerseys
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.46,0:35:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“然后增加球队的收入”\NAnd increase revenue."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.70,0:35:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想：也许这就是事实\N I was like,maybe that's all it is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这就是我在这儿起的作用\NMaybe that's all I'm good for, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.13,0:35:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话我们得对自己坦诚一些\NI think we have to be honest with ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.04,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,签林书豪进来肯定是考虑到了市场因素\NThere was definitely a marketing element to it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是说他是我们自己家乡人\NI mean,he's a hometown guy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.61,0:35:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有很大比重的亚裔人口\NThe area has a significant asian-american population
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.05,0:35:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都证明了确实是那样的\NAnd the way it played out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.35,0:35:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,湾区的球迷为他疯狂\NYou know, people went bonkers for that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.59,0:35:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在许多美国人眼里亚洲人是十分遥远和陌生的\NA lot of what america perceives as asian is very foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.62,0:35:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,姚明是一个典型的例子\N Yao ming was kind of a quintessential example of that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.19,0:35:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他来自中国，他来自东方\NHe's from china, he's from the east
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,到达我们的海岸\NAnd he's coming to our shores
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.33,0:35:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是林书豪却不同 ，他是本土产的\N Whereas,jeremy is like homegrown
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.27,0:35:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在美国本土郊外长大的亚裔小孩\NHe's a homegrown asian-american kid from the suburbs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.40,0:35:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟美国其他小孩一样怀着篮球梦长大 \N He grew up with hoop dreams just like the rest of us
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.21,0:35:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像林书豪这样的孩子在球场上\NSeeing a kid like jeremy on the court
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.71,0:35:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着勇士队的队服 \NIn a warriors uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.38,0:35:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这给我们很大的冲击\NYou know,that's a huge impact
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.65,0:35:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，他很开心能为自己家乡的球队效力\NYou know, he was happy to be playing for his hometown team
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.55,0:36:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，我们并不满足于只是进入NBA\NBut we weren't satisfied with just being in the nba
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.36,0:36:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,球迷想看到林书豪冲到篮下\NFans want jeremy lin to go all the way to the rim
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是球却被抢走了\NAnd he has it taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.00,0:36:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}勇士的管理层\NThe warriors' management{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.40,0:36:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}把林书豪下放到发展联盟\NSent jeremy{\i} {\i1}down to the d-league{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是NBA的小型联盟育才体系\NThe nba's version{\i\i1}of a minor league farm system{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.94,0:36:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他面对着残酷的现实{\i}\N{\i1}He was faced with a harsh reality.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.51,0:36:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,发展联盟是一道难关\NThe d-league is one of the toughest things
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.95,0:36:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对于篮球生涯而言\NWhen it comes to a basketball career.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.25,0:36:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,发展联盟，你懂的，它是个展示的舞台\NThe d- league, you know, it's a showcase
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.29,0:36:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不在乎你赢了多少场\NPeople don't care how many wins you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只在乎你的数据\NAll they care about is your stats.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.02,0:36:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都只与你自己有关，虽然你有队友\NIt's all about you, and you have teammates,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们其实并不和你站在同一战线上\NBut they're not really on your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.43,0:36:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话，他们会抢了你的饭碗\NYou know, they'll take your job if they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.36,0:36:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能抢断？\NYou cut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.63,0:36:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是控卫吗？ \NYou the point guard?\N\N是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.80,0:36:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你把球传给我\NYou pass it to me...\N\N好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.67,0:36:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就在那儿等着\NAnd then just wait out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.20,0:36:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当他去发展联盟的时候，我对他说的话很简单\NWhat I told him when he went to the d-league was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.41,0:36:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把它拿下\NGo kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.74,0:36:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去把发展联盟搞定，然后等着别人给我们打电话\NGo and crush the d-league, and let's get called up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.78,0:36:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是一场战役\NBecause it's a battle, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.65,0:37:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一场意志上的战役\NIt's a battle right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想，"天啊，如果我弄砸了"\NI was like, "man, like, if I play bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.62,0:37:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能就这样了\NThis may be it."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.05,0:37:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪奋力带球\NJeremy lin drives against squeaky,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.59,0:37:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,试图靠近篮架，但把球丢了\Nto get to the rack, throws it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.43,0:37:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡不着觉，因为我压力太大了\NI couldn't really sleep, 'cause I was so stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.40,0:37:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我给我哥哥打电话\NI called my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.83,0:37:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“我现在很纠结”\NI was like, "I'm trippin' right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.27,0:37:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道这是在干嘛\NLike, I don't know what's going on."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想，对他来说，就像是这段旅程\NI think, for him, it was just like the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.74,0:37:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让他筋疲力尽了一样\NWas kind of wearing on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.07,0:37:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这条路上的每一步\N'cause, like, at every step of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.54,0:37:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你都要克服所有这些障碍\NYou have to, like, overcome all these odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.04,0:37:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为，到了某个时间点上\NAnd, like, I think at a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.61,0:37:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这些障碍让他感觉不可逾越\NIt felt insurmountable for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.25,0:37:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他那个时候状态不是很好\NSo he was not in a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.55,0:37:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,林需要稳定下来\NLin needs to settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.22,0:37:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，他快没有力气了\NYeah, he's running out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.95,0:37:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林书豪极力地想要证明{\i}\N{\i1}Jeremy desperately wanted to prove{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.25,0:37:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他属于NBA，但在他的新秀赛季{\i}\N{\i1}That he belonged, but in his rookie year,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.99,0:37:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他被3次下放到了发展联盟{\i}\N{\i1}He was sent to the d-league three times.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.83,0:37:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他被这样送来送去\NI think getting sent back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.30,0:37:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这种经常性来回摇摆的效应\NAnd the constant yo-yo effect
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.27,0:37:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,源于被勇士队调回来\NOf being taken up by the warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.67,0:37:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又下放回去\NSent back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.17,0:38:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其积累性的结果就是给他沉重的负担\NThe cumulative effect of it weighed heavily on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，我一直有那种渴望\NYou know, I've always had that desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.78,0:38:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直有那种渴望在我心中\NAnd I've always had that within me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.38,0:38:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,证明我能在NBA打球\NWhere I want to prove that I could play in the nba.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，你知道，我现在在这里是有原因的\NBut, you know, I'm here right now for a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.08,0:38:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,并且，你知道，神以不同的方式在起作用\NAnd, you know, god works in very different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.82,0:38:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,保持住！保持住！来这儿！\NStay up! Stay up! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.26,0:38:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得随着每场比赛\NYou know,I thought with each game,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.99,0:38:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他的自信心都在增强，并且你能看得到\NHis confidence grew,and you could see it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.56,0:38:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这几乎是伴随着每次场上的持球\NAlmost with each possession up the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在他打了20场比赛的那段时间之后\NAnd after his 20-game stint,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.20,0:38:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他走出了那段发展联盟经历的阴影\NI think he came out of that d-league experience
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.40,0:38:29.53,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(833,390)}埃里克·穆苏曼\N大角羊队主教练（发展联盟）
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.20,0:38:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,开始相信他能在NBA中闯出名堂\NReally believing that he could have an impact in the nba.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.37,0:38:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候很困难，因为我们知道他能打球\NIt was tough, because we knew he could play.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.51,0:38:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让人很沮丧的是，很多人\NIt was just frustrating because so many people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就只想着抛弃他，放弃他\NWere so ready to just bury him and give up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.21,0:38:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说很难\NIt's hard for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.35,0:38:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我真的很热爱篮球\NBecause I really love basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.95,0:38:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是，我爱我的梦想\NLike, I love my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.02,0:38:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的梦想就是打NBA\NMy dream is to play in the nba,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.59,0:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我太想实现这个梦想了，以致于我都无法想象\NAnd I wanted it so bad that I couldn't imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.56,0:38:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在最后快要实现这个梦想的时候，却又马上失去了它\NFinally getting it, and then losing it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.97,0:39:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有人认为詹姆斯现在没有科比强吗？\NDoes anyone in here think lebron is not as good as kobe right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.44,0:39:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为詹姆斯当然没比（科比）强\NI think lebron is definitely not better,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.58,0:39:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是更壮实\NJust bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.45,0:39:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，这有点难讲\NWell, it's kind of hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.78,0:39:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我们知道得更清楚，所以……\NYou'd know better than us, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我也不清楚\NNo, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是坐得比你们近一些而已\NI just had closer seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.56,0:39:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大一些的孩子们？\NOlder kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.80,0:39:34.13,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(661,400)}2011林书豪篮球训练营
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.60,0:39:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你们来这里\NHey, you guys are in here. In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.10,0:39:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,教练：不错，完美\NCoach: Nice, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.74,0:39:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后左边，左边，或者右边，右边。很棒\NAnd then left, left,or a right, right. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.17,0:39:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我喜欢这个\NYeah, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.61,0:39:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一个很好的组\NThis is a good group right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.78,0:39:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，不要动，不要动，不要动，不要动\NHey! Don't move, don't move,don't move, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.61,0:39:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就呆在那儿\NStay out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.91,0:39:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些亚裔孩子，好像，都被我吓坏了\NAll these asian kidsare, like, intimidated by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.15,0:39:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他们讲话，他们就像，”呃……“\Nlike talk to them, they're like, "uh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.42,0:39:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说，”小兄弟，我可不是，科学怪人哦“\NI'm like, "dude, I'm not, like, frankenstein."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.82,0:39:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果对手很高的话，你就会被堵住\NIf they're really tall,you're gonna get stuck,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.52,0:39:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会被判走步\NAnd then you'll get called for a travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.86,0:39:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里\NRight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.43,0:40:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇有些话要说\NRicky has something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.06,0:40:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.26,0:40:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，谢谢你们能来\NNo problem.Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.80,0:40:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得我在发展联盟的时候，我有写日记\NI remember in the d-league, I kept a little diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.80,0:40:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这对你们来说，有点女孩子气\NI know that's a little girlie to some of you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.84,0:40:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但我喜欢写下我的想法\NBut I like to write down some of my thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.30,0:40:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔写一下\NEvery once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.67,0:40:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我可以回顾和想起来\NSo I can look back and remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.24,0:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得在12月29号\NAnd I remember on December 29th,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.18,0:40:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我写到，其实我多么希望\NI wrote about how I actually wish
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有和勇士队签约\NI had never signed with the warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我能放弃篮球，因为我当时无法从中得到乐趣\NI wish I could quit basketball, because I wasn't having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.19,0:40:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我熬过那段日子的是--\NAnd what got me through those times--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,显然，我现在没有那种感受了\NObviously, I don't feel that way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.16,0:40:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但当时让我熬过那段日子的也是\NBut what got me through that time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.46,0:40:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天所有领导者会在这里最重要的原因\NWas the number one reason why all the leaders are here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.86,0:40:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我们想让你们知道\NAnd that's because we want to let you guys know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.93,0:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,神爱我，并且他有一个完美的计划给我\NThat god loves me and that he has a perfect plan for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.44,0:40:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他的计划会带你\NAnd that his plan will take you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.24,0:40:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,经历很多起起落落\NThrough a lot of ups and downs,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.94,0:40:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我一直坚信神\NBut if I stay faithful to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最后，我知道神一定会起作用的\NIn the end,I know that he's gonna work
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.31,0:40:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所有事情都是为了我好\NEverything for my good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.21,0:40:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在当我打篮球的时候\NNow when I play basketball,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.71,0:40:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再为了任何人或事去打球\NI don't play for anybody else anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:40:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只为神打球\NI only play for god.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.52,0:41:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是神给我的目的\NAnd that's the type of purpose that he gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.25,0:41:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他一旦赋予我目的性\NAnd once he gave me that purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.56,0:41:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我获得内心安宁的时候\NThen that's when I had my peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.29,0:41:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦我获得安宁，我就获得了喜悦\NAnd once I got my peace, that's when I got my joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.10,0:41:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}有时候换一种风景{\i}\N{\i1}Sometimes a change of scenery{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.97,0:41:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可以转变对人生的看法{\i}\N{\i1}Can shift a perspective on life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.87,0:41:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说知道我的根是很重要的\NMy roots is important for me to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.91,0:41:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那就代表着我是谁\NBecause it's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.44,0:41:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我身份的很大一部分\NIt's a huge part of my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.91,0:41:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解我的父母来自哪里\NI understand where my parents came from,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.11,0:41:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是如何在那种文化里成长的\NHow they grew up in the culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.42,0:41:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！你把玩偶弄掉了\NOh! Oh! You dropped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.95,0:41:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它弄掉了\NYou dropped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我每年回来的原因\NSo that's why I come back every summer
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.46,0:41:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了好好感受一下\NJust to get a good feel for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.89,0:41:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我的身份感到骄傲\NI'm very proud to be, you know, who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,回到农场\NBack on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.52,0:42:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在还是退后一点吧\NOh, I'm gonna back up a little bit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.31,0:42:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（台语）{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.08,0:42:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看我父亲成长的地方\NSeeing where my dad grew up,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.55,0:42:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以40年间可以发生巨大变化\NSo 40 years makes a huge difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.38,0:42:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，从他在这里成长\NYou know, from him growing up here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.52,0:42:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到我们在美国成长\NTo how we grew up in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.76,0:42:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是一个很卑微的起步\NIt's definitely humble beginnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.36,0:42:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.07,0:43:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.15,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，兄弟，你看到那虾了吗？\NHey, man, you see this shrimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.83,0:43:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，嘿，小心点\NOh, hey, hey. Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.83,0:43:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖父母是在中国出生、长大的\NMy grandparents are born and raised in china.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.90,0:43:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母在台湾出生长大\NMy parents are born and raised in taiwan,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.77,0:43:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在美国出生长大\NAnd I was born and raised in the U.S.,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.84,0:43:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这里面有很多的历史\NAnd so there's a lot of history
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.47,0:43:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的身后有很深厚的文化\NAnd a lot of culture behind who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.38,0:43:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.61,0:43:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}splendid\N( A Whole New World歌词，出自动画片《阿拉丁》）{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.15,0:43:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}tell me, princess{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.62,0:43:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}now when did you last let your heart decide? {i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.99,0:43:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.39,0:43:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1} I can open your eyes{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.83,0:44:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}take you wonder by wonder{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.20,0:44:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}over, sideways, and under{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.07,0:44:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}on a magic carpet ride{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.44,0:44:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{i\1}a whole new world{i\}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.35,0:44:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.20,0:44:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在要去做什么？\NWhat are you about to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.40,0:44:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上要出去\NI'm about to go out here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.47,0:44:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去给一个扣篮大赛当评委\NAnd judge this dunk contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.44,0:44:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后的决赛，冠军赛\NThis is the finale, the championship game,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.07,0:44:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了耐克夏季联赛\NFor the nike summer league,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.51,0:44:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我现在要去做这个了\NSo I'm about to get into this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.31,0:44:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.84,0:44:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我可以讲中文\NThey said I could speak chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.01,0:44:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.69,0:44:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪！\NJeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.59,0:45:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的篮球文化很疯狂\NBasketball culture here is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.40,0:45:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,球迷们很热爱篮球\NThe fans, they love basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.53,0:45:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这里总有人在打篮球\NThere's people playing basketball
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.77,0:45:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,任何时间，在任何球场上\NAll the time on all the courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.07,0:45:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的竞赛水平绝对在提升\NThe level of competition is definitely growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.27,0:45:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能有机会看到这些比赛\NGot a chance to see some games.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.84,0:45:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，你知道，这真是很棒的回归\NSo, you know, it's definitely awesome coming back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.08,0:45:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还看到这项运动（篮球）在这个国家进步了这么多\NAnd seeing how much the sport has grown in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.18,0:45:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,准备，预备，开始！\NReady, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.89,0:45:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想来到这里\NI just think coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.59,0:45:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了很多勤奋努力的人\NI'm seeing a lot of really diligent, hard workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.06,0:45:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到所有人都很用功\NI feel like everybody works very hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.46,0:45:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们做了所有他们能做的事\NAnd they do everything they can
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.83,0:45:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了养活他们自己，还有他们的家人\NTo support themselves and their families,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.33,0:45:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我来说，篮球就是我养活自己和家人的方式\NAnd for me, that way is basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.03,0:45:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为勤奋这种精神是根深蒂固的\NAnd I think hard work is definitely ingrained
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.84,0:45:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在台湾文化里，在中国文化里\NIn taiwanese culture, in chinese culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.44,0:45:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，对我来说，那是一些\NAnd so, for me, that's something
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.98,0:45:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着去学会并且接受的东西\NI try to pick up on and really embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.12,0:46:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哟，兄弟，我们要出发啦\NYo, man, we gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.69,0:46:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪？\NJeremy?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.87,0:46:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在周五早上12点01分\NAt 12:01 Friday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.93,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,NBA停摆了所有的球员\NThe nba locked out its players
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.20,0:46:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为劳资双方无法在新一轮的集体谈判上达成一致\NAfter failing to reach a new collective bargaining agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.27,0:46:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,停摆对很多人有巨大影响\NThe lockout has a very large impact on a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.78,0:46:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,目前放在谈判桌上的条件\NThe current offer that is on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.48,0:46:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我们所能接受的\NIs not one that we can accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.75,0:46:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,停摆可能是几个礼拜\NIt could be a couple weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.81,0:46:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是几个月\NCould be a couple months.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.95,0:46:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经听说\NWe're already hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.28,0:46:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是一个长期的停摆\NThis is gonna be a very long lockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.15,0:46:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将进入NBA的严冬\NWe're about to go into the nuclear winter of the nba.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.59,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,劳资双方的工资谈判过程\NThe collective bargaining process
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.76,0:46:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经完全破裂\NHas completely broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.50,0:46:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都身处其中\NWe're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.70,0:46:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这些球员不给他们\NAnd if these players don't give them
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.06,0:46:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想要的，他们是不会开工的\NWhat they want, they're not going to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.97,0:46:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为这个问题得到了解决\NI don't think it's resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.40,0:46:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是个很糟的建议\NI think it's bad advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.54,0:46:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实私下里\NI actually secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.81,0:46:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这次停摆能继续\NWanted the lockout to continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.31,0:46:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这给了我额外的时间去提高\NBecause it gave me extra time to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.68,0:46:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们愿意继续谈判\NWe are willing to continue discussions
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.71,0:47:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,基于一个有可能性的妥协的基础上\NOn a potential compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.88,0:47:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些老板\NThere are some owners
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.18,0:47:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意走在这个赛季之前\NWho are willing to forego the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.85,0:47:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想要打篮球\NWe want to play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.22,0:47:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我们做的事\NThat's what we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.69,0:47:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我们没有一个机会\NAnd right now, we don't have an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.82,0:47:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去球场上做我们最擅长的事\NTo go out and do what we do best.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.09,0:47:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果整个赛季都没了\NIf we need to lose an entire season,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.23,0:47:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那也只能这么干了\NWe should go ahead and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.13,0:47:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我所有浸满汗水的T恤都在这了\NI got all my sweaty t-shirts in here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.73,0:47:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那太恶心了\NThat's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.10,0:47:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我知道停摆时间越长\NSo I knew the longer the lockout went,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.37,0:47:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会成为越出色的球员\NThe better player I would become.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.81,0:47:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在热身\NWe're warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.14,0:47:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是在热身\NWe're just warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.71,0:47:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样，那一发很完美\NBoom. That's it. That one was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.58,0:47:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好吗？\NFeel good?\N\N感觉很好 \NFeels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.65,0:47:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当他成为一个更好的投手\NAs he gets better as a shooter,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.42,0:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间过去，就像钱，钱，钱一样\NOver time it's gonna be like money, money, money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.96,0:47:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他只会变得越来越好\NHe's only gonna get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.49,0:47:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他真的非常好，难道不是吗？\NAnd he's awfully good now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.00,0:47:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要进入他这个脑袋，那是另外一部分\NThat's the other part, getting into this cranium
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.83,0:47:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让他相信自己，就像我相信他一样\NTo get him to believe like I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.14,0:47:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐，篮球迷们\NMerry christmas, basketball fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.44,0:48:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,NBA重新开赛了\NThe nba is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.84,0:48:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,球迷们就快得到他们梦寐以求的了\NFans are getting what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.21,0:48:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老板们和球员们达成了试行性的协议\NOwners and players reached a tentative agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.64,0:48:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,终结了149天的停摆\NTo end the 149-day lockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.89,0:48:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,进入到我的第二年\NGoing into my second year,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.70,0:48:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\NI'm not really, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.47,0:48:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去想任何让我害怕的事情\NThinking about anything I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.80,0:48:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，我感觉，经历了我的第一年\NYou know, I feel like through my first year,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.11,0:48:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在我眼中\NAt least in my own eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.51,0:48:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经向自己证明，我能在这个水平打球\NLike, I proved to myself that I can play at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.48,0:48:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在心态上，我变得更好了\NAnd I think mentally, I'm at a much better place
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.15,0:48:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我能就这样进去，然后做我自己\NWhere I'm just going in, and I'm just gonna be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.62,0:48:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,打我自己的比赛\NAnd play my own game,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.22,0:48:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从那个立场来看，我真的一点也不畏惧\NAnd from that standpoint, I'm really not afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.65,0:48:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在进入训练营后发生的事情\NOf anything going into training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.89,0:48:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉我已经没有什么可以失去了\NI feel like I have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.03,0:49:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们缺一个感到满意的中锋\NWe didn't have a center that we felt good about,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.13,0:49:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要足够的薪水空间\NAnd we needed to create enough salary cap space
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.14,0:49:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去招揽一个中锋\NTo go make an offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.34,0:49:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这样做，我们要裁掉一些球员\NAnd in order to do so, we had to cut somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.74,0:49:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们做过的决定中\NIt was one of the hardest decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.88,0:49:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,最艰难的决定之一\NThat we could have had to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.01,0:49:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中途给我打电话\NThey called me upmidway through
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.48,0:49:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在训练的中途\NIn the middle of a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.99,0:49:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说，“嘿，你需要到楼上来一趟”\NThey're like, "hey, you got to go upstairs."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.55,0:49:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我走到楼上，然后总经理\NI went in there, and the general manager
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.96,0:49:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和助理总经理说，\NAnd assistant general managerwere like,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.56,0:49:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们得裁掉你”\N"we gotta let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.89,0:49:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们想要德安德鲁·乔丹”\NWe're trying to get deandre jordan."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.39,0:49:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经在赛季前付出了巨大的努力\NHe had worked tremendously hard pre-season,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.86,0:49:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想，“天啊，这是一个大打击啊”\No I was like, "man, this is a blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.90,0:49:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，这就像一脚，刚好踢在你的肚子上\NI mean, this is a kick in the stomach right here."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.84,0:49:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就像\NThey were like,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.14,0:49:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,“哦，我们祝你好运”\N"oh, we wish you the best of luck."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.64,0:49:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“谢谢”\NI was like, "thanks."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.35,0:49:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}48小时后{\i}\N{\i1}Within 48 hours,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.15,0:49:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他被休斯敦火箭队接收{\i}\N{\i1}He was picked up by the houston rockets.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.55,0:49:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们一直在希望\NYeah, we were hoping
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.72,0:49:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他队把他挑走\NThat no one else picked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.26,0:49:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对他感兴趣，已经有很长一段时间了\NWe were interested in him for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.29,0:50:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看过他在哈佛的比赛\NHad been to his games at harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.93,0:50:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候，我们就把他招进来，然后说\NAt the time, we just added him and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.63,0:50:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“嘿，让他加入看看会发生什么”\N"hey, let's bring him in and see what happens."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.40,0:50:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去了休斯敦\NI went to houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.77,0:50:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当时那里有6个控卫\NThere were six point guards there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.24,0:50:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至没法参加训练\NI couldn't even get reps in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.41,0:50:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.08,0:50:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在金州勇士队是个候补控卫\NI was backup point guard at golden state,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.01,0:50:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们把我带到这里\NAnd now they're gonna bring me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.28,0:50:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我成了第六根弦（吉他声音最低的那根弦）？\NAnd I'm sixth string?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.72,0:50:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪在带球\NJeremy lin on the drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.82,0:50:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,把球带到篮筐，然后上篮\NTake it to the rim, lays it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.32,0:50:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在马刺队大个子球员面前的一个好球\NGood shot with the spurs' bigs right in his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.39,0:50:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当火箭队接收了他\NWhen the rockets picked him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.19,0:50:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对于他来说，可能已经是跌入瓶底了\NThat was probably the bottom of the barrel for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.26,0:50:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一个周日晚上，我们在联谊会上\NSunday night, we were in fellowship,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.93,0:50:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得林书豪说，“嘿，我得走了”\NAnd I remember Jeremy said, "hey, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.40,0:50:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“我得赶飞机去休斯顿“\N"I gotta catch my flight to Houston."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.54,0:50:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时站在门口\NHe was standing at the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.27,0:50:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他眼中含泪，因为……\NAnd he had tears in his eyes, because, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.21,0:50:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为压力真的让他难以承受\NBecause the pressure was really getting to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.01,0:50:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他不知道他的未来里还有什么\NHe just didn't know what his future was gonna hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.05,0:50:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得他转向我，然后说\NAnd I remember he turned to me and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.32,0:51:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“我不知道我还能不能继续撑下去”\N"I don't know if I can keep doing this."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.89,0:51:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}仅仅在火箭队待了12天{\i}\NAfter only 12 days with the rockets,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.49,0:51:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他再一次被裁{\i}\N{\i1}He was cut again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.63,0:51:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那天正好是圣诞节\NIt was christmas day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.46,0:51:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,过去几周显然发生了很多事情\NSo obviously a lot has been happening the last couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.50,0:51:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你心里在想什么？\NWhat's going through your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.57,0:51:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天感觉怎么样？\NAnd how you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.74,0:51:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节早上，我被裁了\NChristmas morning, I was waived.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.28,0:51:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞夜，我坐飞机回家\NFlew back home on christmas night,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.78,0:51:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,两周之内，我两次被裁\NAnd within two weeks, I had been waived twice
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.55,0:51:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而裁掉我的两个队说他们还需要我\NBy two teams who said they still wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.32,0:51:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上10点\N10 a.M. This morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.29,0:51:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我得知纽约尼克斯队选了我\NUm, found out the knicks had picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.42,0:51:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,马上我将第一次为尼克斯队上场\NAnd that's gonna be my first game with the knicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.03,0:51:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在甲骨文球馆（金州勇士队主场，林书豪待的第一支NBA球队）\NIt's gonna be at oracle arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.66,0:51:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这场比赛明天晚上就要打了\NYou know, I'm literally going into this game tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.03,0:51:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而我还完全不知道队友有哪些人\NI have no idea who my teammates are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.47,0:51:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未和他们一起打过球\NI've never played with them one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.24,0:51:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不知道我们执行什么战术\NI have no idea what plays we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.97,0:51:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,球队的一个战术也不清楚\NI don't know a single play,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.98,0:51:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还没和教练讲过话\NAnd, you know, I haven't even talked to the coach yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.98,0:52:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这下“好玩”了\NSo it's gonna be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.18,0:52:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪要上场了\NI see jeremy lin coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.12,0:52:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们（尼克斯）今天刚刚签下他\NThey just signed him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.38,0:52:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.58,0:52:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在赛前的投篮练习稍微活动了一下\NWent through a walk-through, at shoot-around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.99,0:52:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,林去年在金州勇士队打过寥寥几场比赛\NLin, who played with golden state last year sparingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.92,0:52:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在发展联盟也打过\NPlayed in the d-league,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.36,0:52:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,欢呼很热烈\NGets a nice ovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.06,0:52:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我绝好的机会\N It's a great opportunity for me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.76,0:52:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能打上球\NTo be able to just play,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.03,0:52:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在对我来说\NAnd I think, for me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.36,0:52:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的一件事\NThe one thing I really care about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.20,0:52:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样一个打球的机会\NIs just an opportunity to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.27,0:52:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我将倾尽全力\NI'm gonna give my best effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.67,0:52:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算最终失败\NAnd, you know, if I go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.61,0:52:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要用我的方式证明自己\NI'm gonna make sure I go down doing it my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.84,0:52:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，也是神的方式\NWhich is god's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.14,0:52:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以比赛前一晚\NSo it's the night before,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.58,0:52:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我打包好了行李\NAnd, you know, I gotta get my bags ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.41,0:52:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的比赛过后，我们将前往洛杉矶\NAnd after the game tomorrow, we head to l.A.,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.98,0:52:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再来是萨克拉门托，然后将飞去纽约，一直待在那里\NSacramento, and then I'm off to new york for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.07,0:52:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,五场比赛过去了，我却一分钟都没上\NFive games go by, and I'm not playing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.84,0:53:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这一切都说不通\NNothing was really making sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.94,0:53:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你签了我\NIf you bring me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.34,0:53:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,却连球队训练也不让我打\NAnd you don't let me play in practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.25,0:53:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,更不要说正式比赛了，那为什么要我呢？\NLet alone the games, then why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.88,0:53:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时觉得，我可以帮助你们\NI felt like, you know, I could help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.88,0:53:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而只能眼睁睁地看着球队输球\NAnd I was watching us lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.32,0:53:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队已经四连败了\NThe knicks have lost four straight games.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.39,0:53:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,连败还在继续\NAnd the losing streak continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.36,0:53:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队已经六连败了\NKnicks have now lost six in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.19,0:53:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队的场上没有很好的化学反应\NThere's a chemistry problem there on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.10,0:53:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要一个控卫来分配球\NThey need a point guard to distribute the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.17,0:53:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林书豪最初的两年合同{\i}\N{\i1}Jeremy's original two-year contract{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.17,0:53:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}即将到期{\i}\N{\i1}Was about to expire,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.70,0:53:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这意味着如果尼克斯队裁掉他{\i}\N{\i1}Which meant that, if the knicks let him go,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.71,0:53:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他不仅得不到薪水，而且，将永远失去机会{\i1}\N{\i1}He'd be dropped with no pay, and, this time, for good.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.64,0:53:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在训练时，书豪站在我旁边\NDuring practice, jeremy was standing right beside me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.80,0:53:43.80,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330,404)}麦克·德安东尼\N尼克斯2008-2012主教练
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.11,0:53:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就站在场边\NOn the side of the court
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.42,0:53:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有加入训练\NAnd not really get in even in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.48,0:53:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他签下来只是\N以防万一哪天有人受伤时顶替的\NHe was just there in case one of these guys got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.96,0:53:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经隐约有预感了\NI pretty much saw the writing on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.02,0:53:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当时就想，“差不多就是这样了”\NI was like, "I'm pretty much done,"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.99,0:53:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能接受现实\NAnd, like, I was resigned to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.73,0:53:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要被裁了\NThat I was gonna get let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.63,0:53:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,站在场边的时候，他走向我\NStanding on the side of the court, he comes up to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.93,0:54:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他说，“嘿，教练，我有一个问题。”\NAnd he goes, "hey, coach, I've got a question."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.00,0:54:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说，“书豪，什么问题？”\NI go, "what is it, jeremy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.37,0:54:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“我在这儿一直都是打出租车的”\N"I'm taking a taxi everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.54,0:54:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,“我应该把我的车带过来吗？”\NShould I ship my car out here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.64,0:54:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当时他的反应是，“呃，也许不必”\NAnd he was like, "uh, you know, probably not."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.21,0:54:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时就想，“完了，又要被裁了“\NI was like, "oh, hell, I'm gonna get waived."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.45,0:54:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就跟助教格兰说\NAnd so I went and talked to glen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.89,0:54:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“格兰，你怎么看？”\NI said, "glen, what do you think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.42,0:54:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他说，“其实我们还没有真正看过他打球”\NAnd he goes, "well, we haven't really seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.66,0:54:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们不清楚”\NWe don't know."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.12,0:54:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“这样吧，我们就让他试试”\NAnd I said, "you know what? Let me try to see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.33,0:54:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果周二之前让他试着打几场比赛”\N"if we can get him in a couple games
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.06,0:54:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“看看会发生什么”\NBefore Tuesday and just see what happens."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.16,0:54:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对我说，“今晚你要上场”\NThey're like, "look, you're gonna play tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.10,0:54:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,“上场之后”\N"I want you to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.70,0:54:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“不希望你做太多事情”\NI don't want you to do too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.24,0:54:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“好的，我不会的”\NI was like, "okay, I won't."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.95,0:54:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,加内特已经得了8分\N8 points for garnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.45,0:54:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪丢球，布拉德利断球上篮得分\NLin coughs it up, bradley to the rim.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.18,0:54:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的没有做很多事\NI didn't do too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.85,0:54:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎什么都没做，我的表现糟透了\NI pretty much did nothing, and I played horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.19,0:54:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,投篮不中\NYou know, I missed shots,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.82,0:54:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,又是失误，又是犯规\NI had turnovers, I had bad fouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.69,0:55:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.73,0:55:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪犯规\NLin reached in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.73,0:55:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想，我最多还有一次机会\NI thought, at most,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.06,0:55:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是下一场比赛\NI had one more chance the next game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.73,0:55:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时想，我刚刚搞砸了和波士顿的比赛\NI was like, "okay, I just screwed the boston game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.27,0:55:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“也许我要被裁了”\N"I probably will get cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.10,0:55:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,“但他们明天可能会再给我一次机会”\NBut they may give me one more chance tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.24,0:55:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那时\NI think at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.88,0:55:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪其实住在他纽约的哥哥那\NJeremy was actually staying with his brother in new york,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.58,0:55:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而在飞机上他跟我说\NAnd he was talking to me on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.46,0:55:26.33,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(807,398)}兰德里·菲尔兹\N后卫，尼克斯2010-2012
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.42,0:55:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚会有一些朋友在我哥那过夜\NHe's like, "you know, my brother, he's got some people over,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.25,0:55:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我可不可以\N"um, so, you know, is it cool
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.89,0:55:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在你家睡一晚上？\NIf I crash at your place instead?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.26,0:55:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，“当然可以”\NYou know, I was like, "yeah, sure, man, you can come."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.99,0:55:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我也有提醒他\NI was giving him forewarning, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.73,0:55:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的沙发不太大\NThat my couch wasn't huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.09,0:55:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个沙发是租来的\NIt was actually a rental couch at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.63,0:55:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多只有六英尺（183厘米）长\NIt might have been maybe six feet long.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.23,0:55:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大概凌晨2点才到\NWe get in at, like, 2:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.24,0:55:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了菲尔兹家\NI go over to landry's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.94,0:55:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他给我看了他的沙发\NHe's like, "this is my couch,"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.24,0:55:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大概这么大\NAnd his couch is like this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.87,0:55:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时就无语了\NI'm like, "dude."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.18,0:55:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能把头挂在沙发一头\NI have my head hanging off of one end
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.04,0:55:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,双脚挂在另外一头\NAnd my legs hanging off the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.98,0:55:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样怎么能睡得好呢？\NI'm like, "oh, my gosh, how am I gonna get a good night's rest?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.42,0:55:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明天还要打球\NLike, "I might play tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.82,0:55:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这也许是我最后的机会\NThis might be my last chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.39,0:56:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得当时对自己说\NI remember thinking to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.62,0:56:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第一，我希望他能上场\NOne, I hope he gets in,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.83,0:56:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他在波士顿的糟糕表现\NBecause he really didn't do enough in the boston game
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.60,0:56:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,无法保证他有足够的上场时间\NTo warrant getting big minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.17,0:56:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,第二，如果他上场，他必须有好的表现\NAnd, two, if he gets in, he's gotta play well,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.07,0:56:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不然这场比赛过后他们就会裁了他\NOr they're gonna release him after the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.77,0:56:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的是\NIt's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.97,0:56:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,本赛季是上次停摆后11、12年内\NThis season was the only season in the \Nlast, like, 11, 12 years since the last lockout
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.06,0:56:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一有连着三场背靠背的赛季\Nwhere people have played back-to-back-to-back games.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.32,0:56:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而尼克斯队只有一次连着三场背靠背\NAnd new york only had one stretch of back-to-back-to-back games.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.32,0:56:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果当时有更多休息时间\NAnd if we had more days to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.42,0:56:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定那场比赛我能否上场\NI'm not sure if I would have been able to play in that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.29,0:56:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我祷告了\NI prayed that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.33,0:56:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祷告是\NAnd my prayer is,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.43,0:56:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“神啊，如果让他打NBA是你的意愿”\N"god, if this is your will for him to play nba,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.07,0:56:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“那么你需要展现给他看”\NYou need to show it."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.84,0:56:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.71,0:57:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,莫罗再次得分\NThere's morrow. Morrow knocks it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.85,0:57:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,德隆投篮\NWilliams sets himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.75,0:57:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,三分命中\NPuts up the 3, and knocks that one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.49,0:57:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队已经落后10分了\NThe knicks find themselves down by 10 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.16,0:57:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队的山姆波特，个人第二次犯规\NNew york foul is on shumpert, his second.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.29,0:57:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看看谁要上场了\NAgain, mike, look who's coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.33,0:57:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是林书豪，你可以听到球迷的大声欢呼\NJeremy lin, and you hear a pretty big ovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.72,0:57:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来没有犹豫\NHe didn't look tentative,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.59,0:57:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有过于忧虑\NHe didn't look overly concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.79,0:57:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来就像在说，“我要放手一搏了”\NHe looked like, "dude, I'm about to go do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.29,0:57:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们裁了我就裁吧\N"if they cut me, they cut me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.46,0:57:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我再也不能在NBA打球也无所谓了\N"if I don't never play another nba game, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.70,0:57:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你们看看真正的林书豪是怎么打球的\NI'm going to play like jeremy lin can play."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.67,0:57:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪突破上篮\NJeremy lin drives and finishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.87,0:58:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的上篮得分\NNice play from lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.14,0:58:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,丢球了\NThere's a strip of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.67,0:58:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪长传给道格拉斯\NLin throws it ahead to toney douglas.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.88,0:58:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,擦板得分\NUp for the layup! Banks it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.35,0:58:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆波特杀过来了，传球给林\NHere comes shumpert to lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.18,0:58:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,林上篮，球进了\NLin flips it up and puts it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.75,0:58:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,又是林书豪！\NJeremy lin once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.42,0:58:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他的半场数据差不多是10+4+4\NHe finished the half with like 10, 4, and 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.69,0:58:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对半场来说很不错了\NLike, good numbers for a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.16,0:58:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,超过了他之前所做的一切\NThat was such a higher high than, like, anything he's, like, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.60,0:58:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时欣喜若狂\NSo I was, like, ecstatic at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.96,0:58:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而到了下半场，他简直\NThe second half, he just went...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.97,0:58:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,简直疯了\NHe just went nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.37,0:58:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（林书豪）突到篮下了，球又进了\NDriving to the basket, does it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.94,0:58:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,同时有加罚的机会\NHe's got a chance for a 3-point play as he got hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.31,0:58:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（林书豪）撞到佩特洛，又杀向篮筐了\NBumped by petro, gets to the rim.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.74,0:58:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,进球有效，还造成对手犯规\NCount it and a foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.44,0:58:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪！\NJeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.51,0:58:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他经历了美妙的一晚\NHe has in one special night
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.72,0:58:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,成了（麦迪逊广场）花园的宠儿\NBecome a garden favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.78,0:58:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚会被人记住吗？\NWill it be remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.95,0:58:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他连着做了\NHe was stringing together,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.29,0:58:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,三个胯下运球\NLike, three crossover moves in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.75,0:58:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,过去他从未这样做过\NLike, things he's never done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.59,0:58:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,（林书豪）再次撕开防守\NSplits the defense again!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.16,0:58:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,杀到篮下了！上篮命中！\NGets to the rim! Pops it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.23,0:58:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还造成犯规！哇！\NAnd a foul! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.33,0:59:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,球迷已经都坐不住了\NAnd the crowd on their feet
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.13,0:59:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来向这个男人致敬\NPaying homage to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.70,0:59:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来连他的队友们\NClyde, even it looks like his teammates
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.47,0:59:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也不相信所发生的一切\NDon't believe what they're seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.50,0:59:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时太兴奋了\NI was just so emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.31,0:59:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们不能把我裁掉了\NThere's no way they can cut me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.44,0:59:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚打了生命中最重要的比赛\NI just had the game of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.55,0:59:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一个胯下运球后杀向篮筐\NAgain, the crossover, the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.55,0:59:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,投篮，又进了\NPuts it up, pops it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.88,0:59:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，25分！\NJeremy lin with 25!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.95,0:59:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,球迷们已经疯狂了！\NAnd this crowd is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.72,0:59:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地突破，玩弄\NPenetrating, manipulating,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.03,0:59:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,完全摧毁了篮网队\NDevastating the nets!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.69,0:59:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来自哈佛的英雄\NHe's the hero from harvard,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.06,0:59:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队终于\NAs the knicks
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.60,0:59:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了一场亟需的胜利，这是他生命中最重要的比赛\NGet a much-needed victory on the game of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.70,0:59:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经被兴奋的队友包围\NAnd he is swarmed by his ecstatic teammates
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.97,0:59:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还有麦迪逊广场花园兴奋的球迷\NAnd a jubilant crowd here at madison square garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.01,0:59:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢神\NI'm just thankful to god
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.71,0:59:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赐予我这次上场的机会\NFor this opportunity to be able to come out here
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.38,0:59:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来为这支球队打球\NAnd play with this team and this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.41,0:59:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.55,0:59:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗了个澡\NMan, I was taking a shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.55,0:59:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至分不清\NAnd I was like... I didn't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.52,0:59:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是洗澡水\NI was like, "is this water, like, from the shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.66,1:00:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我流下的喜悦的泪水\NOr am I actually crying, like, tears of joy?"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.73,1:00:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在是太兴奋了\NOh, I was just, like, so high on emotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.63,1:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我太开心了，我就坐在浴室里\NI was so happy. I was sitting in the shower,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.23,1:00:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,脑子里在回放发展联盟里的那些时光\NReplaying all the times in the d-league,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.44,1:00:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那些我不得不经历的\NAll these flashbacks of these tough times
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.80,1:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,艰苦岁月的片断\NI had to go through.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.11,1:00:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得我出来后\NAnd I remember I got out,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.64,1:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我的家人，他们都在微笑\NI saw my family, and they were all smiling.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.91,1:00:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话给经纪人\NI called my agent,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.21,1:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他在对我大喊大叫\NAnd he was yelling at me on the phone, you know, like,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.65,1:00:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他说，“我太为你骄傲了！我就知道你行的”\N"I'm so proud of you. I knew you could do it."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.22,1:00:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我希望取得的突破\NThat was kind of like the much-needed breakthrough that I was hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.46,1:00:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在林书豪取得对篮网队的惊艳表现之前\NBefore jeremy lin's first big game against new jersey,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.63,1:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他根本不在尼克斯队的计划之内\NHe really wasn't in the knicks' plans at that point,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.30,1:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知\NAnd I'm told they had begun
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.87,1:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们当时已经考虑换掉他了\NTo look seriously at replacements.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.84,1:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,周六晚上的麦迪逊广场花园\NClyde, Saturday night, madison square garden
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.34,1:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和整个赛季一样人声鼎沸\NSounded as loud as we've heard it all season.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.07,1:00:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他无与伦比\NHe was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.74,1:00:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从尼克斯队的角度\NYou just hope from a knicks standpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.05,1:00:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你会希望他能引领进攻\NThat he can run the offense
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.15,1:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,保持周六那样的精彩表现\NAs well as he ran it on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.08,1:00:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次首发我其实没有特别紧张\NI just really wasn't nervous for my first start.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.25,1:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,通常来说，我应该会紧张\NAnd, you know, usually, I would be,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.45,1:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知道为什么我感觉很舒服\NBut I don't know why I just felt really comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.79,1:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,超出自然的平静\NAnd it was just a supernatural peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.69,1:01:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一些我无法解释的事情\NAnd it's one of those things that, you know, I can't really explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.26,1:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}林书豪的第一次NBA首发出场{\i}\N{\i1}For jeremy's first nba start,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.13,1:01:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}阿玛尔·斯塔德迈尔因个人原因缺阵{\i}\N{\i1}Amar'e stoudemire was out for personal reasons,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.77,1:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}卡梅隆·安东尼上半场因伤下场{\i}\N{\i1}And carmelo anthony suffered an injury in the first half.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.94,1:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼走路很艰难\NCarmelo anthony comes up hobbling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.74,1:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他很难受\NHe's in a lot of discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.11,1:01:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在已经不能走路了\NHe can't move right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.98,1:01:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}尼克斯队现在需要一位领袖{\i}\N{\i1}The knicks desperately needed a leader,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.41,1:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}而林书豪将承担起这个使命{\i}\N{\i1}And jeremy would answer the call.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.18,1:01:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪绕过杰弗森\NLin gets around jefferson,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.42,1:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还在看人，上反篮得分\NLooking, and backs it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.75,1:01:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上场比赛有不少这样的表现\NHe had a couple of those the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.02,1:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不断地打挡拆\NWe were running pick and roll
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.56,1:01:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一个挡拆接一个挡拆\NAfter pick and roll after pick and roll.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.86,1:01:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪传给里面的杰弗里斯\NLin inside to jeffries!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.19,1:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他能否保持对篮网那场的表现\NI didn't know how he would follow up, that new jersey game,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.00,1:01:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那场实在太棒了\N'Cause it was such a high,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.43,1:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是（本场比赛）他不断上演各种夸张的上篮\NBut he just kept making ridiculous layups,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.13,1:01:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,各种跳投命中\NHe was hitting jumpers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.54,1:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不了解我的打球习惯\NThey didn't know my tendencies,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.14,1:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不知道我的弱点\NThey didn't know my weak spots,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.87,1:01:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道我的优势和最佳投篮点\NMy strong spots, my sweet spots.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.57,1:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪突进来了\NLin on the drive,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.04,1:01:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拉杆，命中！\NFlips it up, drops it in!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.54,1:02:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,同时造成犯规！好一个反手上篮！\NAnd a foul! Reverse layup!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.58,1:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从未看过我打球\NThey had never seen me play.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.05,1:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,向前推进，传给山姆波特，又回传给林书豪\NPushing it, ahead to shumpert, back to lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.92,1:02:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,林被打到了，球还是放进，2+1！\NLin gets hit, puts it in, and a foul!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.02,1:02:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,上篮\NLays it up, puts it up,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.36,1:02:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还是活球\NChandler keeps it alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.62,1:02:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,林必须得投了\Nlin has to put it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.39,1:02:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在进攻24秒结束前三分命中\NA 3-pointer as the shot clock expired!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.46,1:02:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我像压榨秘书似的使用他\NI'm riding him like friggin' secretariat.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.07,1:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪\NJeremy lin
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.30,1:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,连续两个职业生涯的重要夜晚\NWith his second consecutive career night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.91,1:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在是尼克斯队新的首发控卫\NHe is the new starting point guard of the knicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.58,1:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队再次取胜\NAnd the knicks win again.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.51,1:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全场观众起立向林书豪致敬\NA standing ovation for jeremy lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.06,1:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,过程中有非常多细微的因素\NYou know, there's so many little variables
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.86,1:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是我无法掌控的\NWith every step of the way being something I can't control.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.50,1:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,比如，休斯顿火箭队晚了一天才裁掉我\NYou know, houston waives me a day late.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.20,1:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们早一天裁掉我\NIf they waive me a day earlier,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.83,1:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就会超过裁人的线\NI would have been past the waiver wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.44,1:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那天早上山姆波特正好受伤\NShumpert gets hurt that morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.74,1:03:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队才选了我\NThe knicks pick me up,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.14,1:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为去年他们试训过我\NBecause they had worked me out the year before.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.18,1:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,正好，尼克斯队的主教练是德安东尼\NYou know, it happens to be d'antoni who's coaching here
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.81,1:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的进攻体系就像是为我量身打造的\NWhose offense is tailor-made for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.82,1:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,突然之间，一切都变得疯狂了\NAnd all of a sudden, things just go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.32,1:03:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两场他平均得分26.5分\NHe's averaging 26 1/2 points a game the last two games.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.89,1:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这不可持续\NI don't think that's gonna continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.56,1:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这显然无法持续\NObviously, that's not gonna continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.69,1:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接着我们踏上客场之旅，前往华盛顿\NThen we hit the road and go to washington,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.76,1:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又将遇上约翰·沃尔\NAnd it's like john wall again, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.10,1:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,夏季联赛的时候我和沃尔交过手\NLike, I played against john wall in the summer league,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.70,1:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在狭路相逢\NAnd now it's, like, a rematch.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.24,1:03:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又要和他对位\NNow I'm playing against him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.57,1:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,呜~\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.67,1:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪突破到禁区内\NLin on the drive, gets inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.64,1:03:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪反手上篮，漂亮！\NReverse layup. Great play by jeremy lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.18,1:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔杀过来了，看着\NHere comes wall. Look at wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.65,1:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,撕开防守\NBreaks the press,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.85,1:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,左手暴扣\NAnd throws it down with the left hand!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.29,1:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时的反应是，靠，他居然在我头上扣篮\NI was like, "dang, he kinda dunked on my head."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.06,1:03:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须还以颜色！\NI was like, "I'm gonna try to get him back."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.89,1:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,几个回合过后，他们的防守出了问题\NCouple possessions later, they messed up their coverage,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.56,1:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我轻松地突进去\NI had a free lane,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.00,1:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就试着去扣扣篮\NAnd I just tried to take the rim down.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.73,1:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪突破！\NLin drives!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.03,1:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是你说的扣篮\NThere's the dunk you're talking about, clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.84,1:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪点燃球迷的激情\NJeremy lin fires up the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.64,1:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到这么大的空当\NWhen I saw that opening,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.11,1:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是用尽全力去完成那记扣篮\NI just tried to dunk it as hard as I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.04,1:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know. There's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.85,1:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有太多的痛苦和磨炼\NThere's been so much pain and so many trying times,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.38,1:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在终于能打上球了\NAnd now that I get to play,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.79,1:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想把这些都宣泄出来\NI'm just letting it all out, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.65,1:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把一切都宣泄在球场上\NI'm just letting it all out on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.56,1:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛过后，当我回想时\NAfter the game, I just look back,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.66,1:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得很有趣\NAnd I'm like, "man, that was so fun."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.50,1:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一个美妙的故事正在酝酿，主角是林书豪\NThe great story that's brewing is jeremy lin,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.60,1:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.93,1:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他本年度的合同算是有保证了\NAnd this week, contracts are guaranteed for the rest of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.80,1:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.97,1:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他的球场表现就像在说，“让他的价值充分展现”\N（电影《甜心先生》的台词）\NHe's been balling out, saying, "show that man his money."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.07,1:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.17,1:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有一点可以肯定，他在场上的视野很好\NThe things that's for real is his vision,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.34,1:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这不会变\NWhich won't change,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.57,1:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他的速度不会变\NHis speed, which won't change,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.08,1:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他对比赛的认知不会变\NHis knowledge of the game, which won't change.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.48,1:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是觉得不会变\NI just don't see it changing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.98,1:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要再引用我的话了\NNow, again, please don't quote me on that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.02,1:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼·史密斯：现在他该出现在球探报告里了\NKenny Smith: Now he's on the scouting report.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.38,1:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沙奎尔·奥尼尔： 是的，当然\NShaquille o'neal: Yeah, he is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.02,1:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看他是否在洛杉矶湖人队的球探报告里\NLet's see if he's in the scouting report for the lakers
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.65,1:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，周五晚上，关注麦迪逊广场花园\NOh, yeah, he is. On Friday night at the garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.12,1:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两周我就是睡这里的\NThis is basically where I lived the last two weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.56,1:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,睡在这张沙发上\NAnd so it's the couch I slept on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.57,1:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的哥哥和大嫂\NUh, my brother and sister-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.47,1:05:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地招待了我\NUh, did a good job of hosting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.31,1:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心\NHad a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.37,1:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.81,1:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们的小弟弟就要搬出去了\NAnd now their little kid might have to move out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.71,1:05:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.95,1:05:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我现在不洗衣服\NIf I don't do laundry now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.81,1:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我结婚了也不会洗，没错\NI won't do laundry when I'm married. Fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.85,1:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大嫂：你们脏死了\NSister-in-law:You guys are brats.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.59,1:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会做别的事情\NSo? We do other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.02,1:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.42,1:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大嫂：比如？\NSister-in-law: Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.96,1:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.99,1:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么比如不比如的\NWhat do you mean, like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.76,1:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该问有什么是我们不做的\NLike, what don't we do, is the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.70,1:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大嫂：那你会做什么？\NSister-in-law: What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.86,1:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈： {\i1}你 {\i}会做什么？\NShirley: What do {\i1}you{\i} do?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.43,1:05:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都午睡\NI take a nap every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.63,1:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈：是的，这个我了解\NShirley: Yeah, that I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.90,1:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有很多人能做到这个\NWho does that? Not many people can.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.77,1:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有很多人可以\NNot many people can.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.34,1:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是个吃货\NAnd you eat a lot,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.47,1:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一天到晚吃个不停\NNonstop all day long. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.14,1:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天，总经理跟我说\NYesterday, the general manager was like,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.01,1:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪，你的合同有保障了\N"hey, jeremy, by the way, you're guaranteed now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.75,1:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要睡沙发了\NSo get off the couch."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.68,1:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我......\NI was like...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.85,1:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈：他其实有地方住\NShirley: This guy has a place to stay,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.09,1:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他不想住那\NBut he doesn't want to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.29,1:06:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只想赖在这里\NHe want to crash in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.79,1:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可不想这个上新闻\NThey don't want this to be on the news,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.59,1:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪睡在他哥哥的沙发上\NJeremy sleeping on the couch at his brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.13,1:06:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.80,1:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了\N It's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.30,1:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了\NIt's just crazy to...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.17,1:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你吧，我的社交网络，我的手机\NI'm telling you, social media, Twitter, facebook, my phone, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.64,1:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.50,1:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还能不能更疯狂\NI don't know if it could get crazier than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.98,1:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\NLike, I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.74,1:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪？\NJeremy lin?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.88,1:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有听说过吗？\NAre you following that story at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.05,1:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道，听过一下\NNo idea. I know who he is,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.05,1:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我真的不太清楚状况\NBut I don't really know what's going on too much with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.45,1:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你对林书豪过去一周的表现感到震惊吗？\NAre you surprised at the production that lin's had over the past week?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.85,1:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.15,1:06:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不知道他做过什么\NI don't even know what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.99,1:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不知道你们说的是哪个人\NLike, I have no idea which you guys are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.13,1:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.13,1:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了一些报道\N I'm reading all these quotes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.26,1:06:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,关于他（科比）说了什么\NAbout what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.83,1:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,“科比完全不知道林书豪是何人”\N"kobe bryant has no idea who jeremy lin is."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.40,1:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的反应是，“什么”？\NI'm like, "what?"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.87,1:06:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想，“你为什么要这么说”\NI'm like, "why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.27,1:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,“我完全没有谈论你”\N"I didn't say anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.67,1:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“从没说过你的坏话”\NI never talked bad about you."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.61,1:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以听说这件事时，我心想……\NSo when I heard that, I was like...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.54,1:07:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.71,1:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,“球场上见”\N"here we go."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.38,1:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你会单防他吗？\NWould you consider guarding him
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.15,1:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他的表现很好？\NIf he's having one of those games?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.19,1:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.32,1:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不要着急\NLet's not get ahead of ourselves here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.46,1:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,加油！\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.73,1:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,新的英雄已经出现\NThere is a new man in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.30,1:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,狭路相逢勇者胜\N"may the best man lin(win)."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.43,1:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的竞猜，林书豪能否超过23分\NOver-under, 23 points for lin tonight, bomani.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.24,1:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对手是内线长人如林的湖人队\NAgainst the lakers with those trees they've got inside?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.74,1:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不会有那么多林疯狂时刻了\NIt won't be so linsane tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.91,1:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚谁得分高？科比还是林书豪？\NKobe or lin? Who scores more tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.98,1:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我选林书豪，我的英雄\NI'm going with my guy, jeremy lin, my hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.68,1:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.91,1:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他无所不“林”\NBecause all he does is lin, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.18,1:07:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,短短一周\NJeremy lin in just one week
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.82,1:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪就改变了一切\NHas turned things around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.25,1:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,无论对他自己还是尼克斯队来说\NFor his career and for the new york knicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.66,1:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱林书豪，太棒了！\NI love it! It's awesome, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.26,1:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是纽约发生过最美妙的事情\NThis is like the greatest thing that's happened to new york ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.69,1:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这么一个夜晚\NIt's one of those nights,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.86,1:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一个故事\NAnd it's one of those stories
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.10,1:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们知道为何如此热爱体育\NWhere it really is why we love sports.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.03,1:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道结果会怎样\NI didn't know how it was gonna turn out,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.27,1:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\NBut I was like,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.60,1:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我将非常非常具有攻击性\N"I'm just gonna be really, really aggressive."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.38,1:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的比赛进行得很顺利，投篮都弹无虚发\NEverything was going well, everything was going down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.02,1:08:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪跳投，命中！\NLin puts it up, puts it in!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.52,1:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的开局\NTerrific start!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.89,1:08:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,听听球迷的欢呼吧！\NAnd listen to this garden crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.86,1:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我记最让我激动不已的是\NI think the one thing where I kind of lost it a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.53,1:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.67,1:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看着他带球，突然急停转身\NHe'd come down, he kind of like stutter-stepped, and spun
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.80,1:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,手指很柔软地轻轻一投\NAnd finger-rolled it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.60,1:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,林喜欢这个大空当\NLin likes the open floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.94,1:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,转身，投篮，命中！\NSpinning, puts it up and puts it in!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.64,1:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，超级精彩的得分\NSensational play for jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.94,1:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,整个球馆都沸腾了，在这样一个全国瞩目的舞台\NThe garden erupted, and to do it on the national stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.45,1:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人看过之后都永生难忘\NAnybody who saw that moment will never forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.38,1:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,, 又一次点燃了麦迪逊广场花园\NElectrifying the garden again!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.29,1:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经得了18分了\NHe's got 18 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.06,1:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到演播室，这是林书豪的半场个人表演\NWelcome to our studios for the jeremy lin toyota halftime show.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.83,1:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪是顶级的\NJeremy lin was superb,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.93,1:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,投篮12中7\N7 of 12 from the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.66,1:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下18分5次助攻\N18 points, 5 assists.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.30,1:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,科比和他的队友的投篮手感还很差\NKobe bryant and the lakers struggling shooting the ball,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.70,1:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在他们还只落后8分\NBut they're only down by 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.50,1:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,科比，一系列假动作\NBryant, a couple of fakes,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.31,1:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要投篮了，球进了\NGonna put it up, and knocks it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.78,1:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪抢断\NStripped by lin, stolen by lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.18,1:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,助攻左侧的山姆波特，左手上篮命中！\NLeft side, shumpert, left-handed layup!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.22,1:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,科比转身，高难度的一球\NBryant spinning, difficult shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.69,1:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.29,1:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,又是科比\NKobe bryant again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.39,1:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他要开始接管比赛了\NHe is starting to get in one of those zones right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.89,1:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,加索尔在防守林书豪\NGasol is on lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.36,1:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一个两分球，进了！\NPuts up the 2-pointer. Puts it in!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.93,1:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪31分！\NJeremy lin with 31!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.77,1:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,杰弗里斯抢下篮板\NAnd the rebound by jeffries.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.87,1:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪三分\NLin for 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.58,1:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,梆！\NBang!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.61,1:09:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,三分命中\N3-pointer!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.01,1:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪！\NJeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.22,1:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我整年最喜欢的一次得分\NAnd my favorite play of this whole year
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.99,1:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个底脚的三分\NWas when I hit that 3 in the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.99,1:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那场比赛有太多的渲染\NJust because that game had so much hype,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.96,1:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那记投篮就像一把匕首\NAnd that shot was kind of the dagger
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.30,1:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,狠狠地给了他们一刀\NThat put the game out of reach for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.86,1:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,本赛季两次被裁\NAlready cut twice this season,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.10,1:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为无处可去而只能睡在队友的沙发上\NSleeping on a teammate's couch, because he had nowhere else to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.24,1:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而一夜之间，他成了曼哈顿的宠儿\NAnd, suddenly, jeremy lin is the toast of manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.74,1:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里\NThis is it right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.04,1:10:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的梦想\NThis is my dream, and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.21,1:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我感谢神\NI'm just thankful to god, man,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.01,1:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让我美梦成真\NBecause this is my dream being lived out,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.58,1:10:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我无比感恩\NAnd I'm so thankful for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.25,1:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪38分\NJeremy lin, 38 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.88,1:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,本赛季尼克斯队球员的得分新高\NIt's the most by a knick this season.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.65,1:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“林疯狂”还在麦迪逊广场花园继续\NLinsanity continues here in madison square garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.02,1:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的难以形容\NIt's indescribable, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.36,1:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未见过这样的事情\NIt's something I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.56,1:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有预料到\NI didn't foresee this coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.76,1:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\NYou know, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.37,1:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人会很奇怪\NThis is, like, how weird I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.57,1:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时想这场比赛之后我要出口气\NI was like, "I'm gonna go off this game,"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.64,1:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,采访结束时，他们肯定会问我\NAnd at the end of the interview, they're gonna be like,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.54,1:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得科比现在认识你了吗？\N"oh, so do you think kobe knows who you are now?"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.41,1:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,书豪，你知道肯定有个人会问你这个问题\NJeremy, you knew somebody was gonna ask you this,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.98,1:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为科比现在认识你了吗？\NBut do you think kobe knows who you are now?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.11,1:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们问我那个问题\NIf they ask me that question,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.58,1:10:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的回答会是，“科比？谁啊？”\NI'm gonna be like, "who the hell is kobe?"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.35,1:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想这样回答\NThat's what I was gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.92,1:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想了一会儿\NAnd then I, like, thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.55,1:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,祷告的时候\NAnd I prayed about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.02,1:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想想神会怎么做呢？\NI was like, you know, "what would jesus do?"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.62,1:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不，神应该不会这么说\NAnd I'm like, "jesus probably wouldn't say that,"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.76,1:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要改变我的答案\NSo I was like, "I'm gonna change my answer."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.63,1:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“这得问科比本人了”\NAw, well, you guys have to ask kobe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.00,1:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.63,1:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来看看当今体育界最大的新闻：林书豪\NLet's get to what matters in sports today, jeremy lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.00,1:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪现在是纽约的第一巨星\NRight now, the biggest star in new york is jeremy lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.57,1:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你不关注体育也一定听过他的故事\NI don't even think you have to\Nbe a sports fan to hear about this story.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.04,1:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.24,1:11:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“林旋风”横扫纽约全城\NNew york has a raging case of linsanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.21,1:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是疯狂的时刻\NThat's what it is right now. It's madness right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.61,1:11:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪\NJeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.62,1:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,无所不“林”\NAll I do is lin, lin, lin.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.29,1:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样？\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.55,1:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得现在的一切如何？\NWhat do you think about all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.02,1:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,疯狂，太疯狂了\NUm, it's crazy. It's just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.29,1:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在体育界最大的头条\NOne of the biggest headlines
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.93,1:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是“林疯狂”\NIn sports right now is linsanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.33,1:11:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没听说过他？你会的\NIf you haven't caught it yet, you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.16,1:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“林疯狂”席卷纽约城\NLinsanity takes new york by storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.20,1:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他实在是尼克斯队没有办法的办法了\NHe was a last-ditch effort for the knicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.27,1:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当时的情况可能是，有人说，“今晚谁想上场吗？”\NThey sort of said, "all right, who wants to play?"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.30,1:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他举起了手，然后就有人说，“那好，你上吧”\NAnd he raised his hand and, "all right, get in there."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.77,1:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么多年报道体育以来前所未闻的事情\NI have never seen anything like this in all my years of covering sports.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.04,1:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.58,1:12:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,从为见过一个人从默默无闻\NI've never seen somebody go from a no-name
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.65,1:12:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在两周之内成为一个轰动的现象\NTo an absolute phenomenon inside of two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.98,1:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太难以置信了\NIt's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.55,1:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他有魅力、有型、有天赋\NHe's doing it with charisma, with style, with flair,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.62,1:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，他还打得很开心\NAnd he's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.26,1:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这很疯狂，火得不行\NIt's crazy. It's catching fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.93,1:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得“林疯狂”这个词\NLinsanity, I think it'll probably be
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.13,1:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,将会收录到下一版的字典里\NIn the dictionary in the next version.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.03,1:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,林疯狂？我爱林疯狂\NLinsanity? I love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.76,1:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱林疯狂，我为他感到高兴\NI love linsanity. I'm so happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.07,1:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪（过去三场）得了89分\NJeremy lin's 89 points,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.64,1:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是所有球员自NBA和ABA合并以来\N职业生涯前三场首发合计最高分\NThe most by any player in his first\Nthree pro starts since the aba-nba merger.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.41,1:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,传给外面的林，林面对里德诺胯下运球\NOutside to lin, crosses over ridnour,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.04,1:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,投篮命中\NAnd hits.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪空中连线菲尔兹\NJeremy lin up top to fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.48,1:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,林迅速杀到篮下\NLin a whirling dervish right to the rim,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.25,1:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,左右腾挪完成上篮\NZigzagging to the cup.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.25,1:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队又取得一场胜利\NThe knicks have stolen one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.35,1:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,赛季最长的五连胜\NIt's their fifth straight win, their longest of the season.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.16,1:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,您已经不是哈佛最有名的毕业生了\NYou have been surpassed as the most\N famous person who is a harvard graduate.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.06,1:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.56,1:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实比你们更早知道林书豪\NI knew about jeremy before you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.53,1:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您的意思是“林疯狂”也有您的功劳？\NAre you taking credit for linsanity?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.17,1:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得您有点这个意思\NIt kind of feels like you are a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.33,1:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有功劳\NI can't take credit for it,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.60,1:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思只是，我比你们更早认识了他\NBut I'm just saying I was there early.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.34,1:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所说，这是很棒的故事\NAs you said, it's a great story.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.14,1:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说，哪一部分最棒？\NWhat's the greatest part in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.41,1:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们取得五连胜\NThat we've won five in a row.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.81,1:13:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.05,1:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对我个人来说是这样\NThat's it for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.35,1:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的一切\NUh, just everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.52,1:13:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是体育的魅力\NJust here's just what's right with sports.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.39,1:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,从默默无闻到一举成名\NHe's an underdog that came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.69,1:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他很好地做到了\NHe does it the right way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.96,1:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他够格打NBA吗？当然，毫无疑问\NCan he play in the nba? Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.89,1:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他全面，打得也很好\NHe's got all the tools, and he's playing really well.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.26,1:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是侥幸，他有实力\NThat's not a fluke, how he's playing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.57,1:13:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当时场边有个人\NI had this one dude courtside
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.50,1:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,整场比赛都在对我大吼大叫\NWho was just yelling at me the whole game.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.44,1:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“你只能持续一周罢了”\NHe's like, "you're a one-week wonder."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.37,1:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“这场比赛你就会输了，你逊毙了”\NYou know, "you're not gonna win this game. You suck."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.68,1:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那场打得很糟糕\NWe were playing bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.85,1:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,全队都很疲惫\NWe were tired, and I was like,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.35,1:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,“这将是一场艰难的比赛”\N"man, this is gonna be a tough one to pull out."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.28,1:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛剩一分钟时我们还落后五分\NWe were down 5 with a minute left.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.82,1:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一次关键的抢断\NYou know, we got this huge steal,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.92,1:13:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,扣篮，还落后三分\NLayup, down 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.19,1:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们进攻没打成，我们有喘息的机会\NThey're coming down, we get a stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.19,1:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,阿米尔·约翰逊那个加罚球\NThe and-1 at amir johnson
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.40,1:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,拉平了比分，他个人已有5个盖帽\Nwho I believe had 5 blocks to that point, ties the game.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.27,1:14:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪假投三分，改为突破\NLin fakes the 3, drives,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.10,1:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,突进去上篮了\NGoes in for the layup,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.24,1:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,球进了，还造成犯规！\NIt's good, and a foul!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.17,1:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪有机会通过罚球扳平比分\NLin can tie it with a free throw.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.07,1:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,, 当时球没进\NThey come down, missed shot,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.68,1:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拿到球，比赛差不多还有20秒\NAnd now we got the ball with, like, 20 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.41,1:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,林传给山姆波特\NLin to shumpert,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.91,1:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆波特跳投\NShumpert, pull-up jump shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.55,1:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没进，钱德勒抢到篮板\NWon't go, Chandler the rebound.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.55,1:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队将耗尽时间，完成最后一投\NAnd the knicks will hold it for the final shot
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.02,1:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,24秒进攻倒计时已经关闭\NAs the 24-second clock is shut off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.46,1:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,德安东尼没有叫暂停\NMike d'antoni won't call time out
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.06,1:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,猛龙队做好了防守准备\NAnd let the raptors set up their d.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.20,1:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,加拿大航空中心的观众都站起来了\NThe crowd on its feet here at the air canada centre.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.00,1:14:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪跳投\NLin puts it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.47,1:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,梆！！\NBang!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.07,1:14:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪，三分命中！\NJeremy lin from downtown,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.41,1:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克斯队取得领先！\NAnd the knicks take the lead!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.68,1:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太惊人了！\NAmazing here at the air canada centre!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.28,1:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩10秒钟，所有人都站起来了\N10 seconds, everyone standing,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.88,1:14:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,全场有2万人\N20,000 in toronto.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.49,1:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拉开拉开！\NGet out of his way!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.25,1:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让他单挑卡尔德隆！\NLet him just take calderon himself!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.36,1:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩3秒钟，林书豪有身高优势\N Three seconds, lin sizes him up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.19,1:15:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,干拔三分命中！\NStraightaway 3, buries it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.66,1:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只留下0.5秒钟\N.5 remaining!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.33,1:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“林疯狂”还在继续！\NLinsanity continues!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.60,1:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我对结果很满意\NI'm just glad it went like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.23,1:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让林疯狂能够稍微冷却一点\NSo we can calm the linsanity down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.60,1:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.34,1:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法阻挡\NWhere we couldn't get a stop...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.24,1:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.58,1:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦寐以求的，就是投进这样的制胜球\NThat's all I dream about is hitting the game winner
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.75,1:15:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再摆出搞怪的动作\NAnd then doing some cool little dorky pose
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.28,1:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后帅气地走回去\NAnd then walking off.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.82,1:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,像我小时候那样\NYou know, that's, like, all I did growing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.09,1:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想这么做\NI always wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.32,1:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道那是什么感觉\NI wanted to know what that felt like.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.36,1:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他有能力\NHe's got the game,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.13,1:15:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他态度很好，他很拉风\NHe's got the attitude, he's got the swag.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.03,1:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么都有\NHe's got all of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.06,1:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.16,1:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\NOkay. "thank you for being..."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.63,1:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我直接开始第一部分？\NOr do I just do the first part?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.17,1:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\NYeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.27,1:15:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，书豪，呃，我是说.......\N"hey, jeremy..."I mean...Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.44,1:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's driving me out of my mind{\i}\N{\i1}（Bell Biv Devoe《Poison》的歌词）{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.44,1:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要拨打电话\N"just dial star-star-knicks on your iphone or android phone..."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.68,1:15:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.25,1:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或登录尼克斯队官网\NOr go to nyknicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.12,1:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can't get it outta my head{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.82,1:16:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}head{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.05,1:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that girl is poison{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.02,1:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.49,1:16:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.39,1:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,完美\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.56,1:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所有印度尼西亚的朋友\N"to all my friends in indonesia..."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.26,1:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所有新加坡的球迷\N"to all my fans in singapore..."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.16,1:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界的球迷\N"to all my fans around the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.70,1:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的支持\NThank you for all your support."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.67,1:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.77,1:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,林疯狂的魅力甚至绕过半个地球到了台湾\NLinsanity is catching on even halfway around the world in taiwan,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.27,1:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,点燃了台湾球迷的激情\NEven halfway around the world in taiwan,Igniting a crowd in taipei that went to a bar
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.94,1:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在早上8点钟去酒吧看他的比赛\NAt 8:00 in the morning to watch him on tv.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.45,1:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（葡萄牙语）{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.28,1:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（日语）{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.39,1:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（西班牙语）{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.61,1:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他把一切都处理得很好\NHe's handled everything very well,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.35,1:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,像你说的，镇定自若\NAs you said, unflappable,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.82,1:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果还要挑刺的话\N（chink in the armor：俗语，带有对中国人的嘲讽意味）\NBut if there is a chink in the armor,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.68,1:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他还应该在哪些方面提高？\NWhere can lin improve his game?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.55,1:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Chink in the armor...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.05,1:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,\Na chink in the armor...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.59,1:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很强壮，臂展很长\NNice build, he's got long arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.12,1:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个合格控卫需要具备的\NThat's what you need as a point guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.39,1:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他实在是\NAnd he's really, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他的眼神呢？（暗讽亚洲人的眼睛小）\NWhat about his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.30,1:17:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,迷离\NDreamy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.40,1:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他的视野很好\NHe has great court vision.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.40,1:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不用Lin做双关语\NTake away the lin puns...Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.30,1:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,结果是这样的\NThis is what you end up with.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.64,1:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊“亚”\N{\i1}（"Amasian": amazing和asian的合体）{\i}\N"amasian."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.24,1:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这......\Nnow is that even...now is that even...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.34,1:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这合法吗？\Nnow is that even...Is that even legal?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.87,1:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，这是林书豪\NJeremy lin. Yes, that's real.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.51,1:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他是从幸运饼干里蹦出来的\N（幸运饼干：美国中餐厅常见食品）\NJeremy lin coming out of a fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.11,1:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切证明我们是多么措手不及\NThis whole thing has shown how unprepared
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.82,1:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来面对这种文化\NWe were to deal with this culture in this context.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.95,1:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Floyd Mayweather（黑人拳击手）在推特上评论林书豪说\NFloyd mayweather on jeremy lin tweets...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.29,1:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这些炒作不过因为他是亚裔\N"all the hype is because he's asian.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.43,1:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,黑人球员每晚都有他那样的表现\N"black players do what he does every night
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.29,1:17:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,却没有得到同等的称赞\NAnd don't get the same praise."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.80,1:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，我认为他的话是种族歧视\NFirst of all, what he said I think is racist.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.70,1:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他不但可以在NBA立足\NNot only can he compete and make it in the nba,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.23,1:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他还不断创造纪录\NThe guy's tearing it up and is breaking records, you knucklehead.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.70,1:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这张图，他用数学取得胜利\NCheck it out. "he does the math to win."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.27,1:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\Nyeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.68,1:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对亚裔的很多观念根深蒂固\NFor many years, we've had many stereotypes about asian-americans,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.53,1:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一窝蜂全出来了\N我们还都觉得这些都是小意思\NAnd now they're all kind of coming\Nout like they're no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.53,1:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它们很要紧\NThey are a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.18,1:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天终于来了\NAnd that'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.55,1:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,（尼克斯队）的连胜终止\NThe winning streak comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.39,1:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,以令人失望的方式\NIn disappointing fashion,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.65,1:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,新奥尔良黄蜂队\NAs the new orleans hornets
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.22,1:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让林书豪和尼克斯队吞下\N林书豪时代以来第一场失利的苦果\NHand jeremy lin and the knicks their first loss in the jeremy lin era.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.86,1:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在变得更简单了\NNow it's easier for me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.46,1:18:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人说了种族歧视的话\NSomeone will say something racist,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.03,1:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一笑而过，觉得很有趣\NAnd I'll laugh, and I'll think it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.07,1:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把所有负面的东西\NEverything I get now, like, all the negative stuff,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.34,1:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都放到一个地方\NI'll just put it in one place
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.97,1:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把它们变成积极的东西\NAnd turn it into positive stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.47,1:18:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让我正确地使用\NSo that I could use it the right way,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.87,1:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当我带着愤怒打球，我就会打得很烂\NAnd when I play out of anger, I play horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.01,1:18:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我学会控制自己的情绪\NAnd so I had to learn how to control my emotions
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.15,1:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让它随风而去\NAnd then just, like, let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.66,1:19:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,手不要受伤\NDon't break your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.78,1:20:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？尼克斯队的林书豪\NSo did you know that new knicks sensation, jeremy lin,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.15,1:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个弟弟现在才大一，也打控卫\NHas a brother who's a freshman point guard
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.79,1:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是汉密尔顿学院\NFor hamilton college?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.09,1:20:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当然知道，不过就算不知道\NWe did, though even we didn't know
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.72,1:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在今天的分区决赛上\NThat today's continental home finale
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.12,1:20:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到林书豪的整个家庭都来了\NWould bring out the entire lin clan,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.03,1:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,包括林书豪本人\NIncluding the linsational jeremy himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.79,1:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他会来看我的比赛\NI did not know he was coming to my game,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.76,1:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在学校里确实听到有人这样说\NAnd I actually heard from a couple people on campus like,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.44,1:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,“嘿，听说你哥要来”\N"hey, your brother's coming."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.64,1:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的反应是，“不，他不会来的”\NI was like, "no, he's not."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.94,1:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有过\NI've never really had that before,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.64,1:20:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一场比赛有那么大的关注\NHad that kind of hype around one of my games.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.52,1:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这并没有很大区别\NBut I didn't see it as that big of a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.05,1:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过就是家人来看我的比赛\NIt was just my family watching my game, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.65,1:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在“林疯狂”之前他就有来看过\NI mean, he did come down before linsanity happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.02,1:21:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前，他来看比赛时\NHe had come down to watch my games before that,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.36,1:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有人会关心\NAnd no one really cared.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.83,1:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两年\NFor the last, like, two years,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.27,1:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他在球场上一直郁郁不得志\NHe was never enjoying himself out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.00,1:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,直到与篮网队的那场比赛过后\NBut that new jersey game, when things were rolling,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.41,1:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次觉得，他在享受比赛\NFor the first time, he was just, like, having fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.64,1:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,活在自己的梦想之中\NLiving his dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.21,1:21:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这才是“林疯狂”给他带来的，最美好的东西\NI think that was, like, the best thing from linsanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.72,1:21:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在最重要的问题是：“林疯狂”能继续吗？\NThe big question now is, can linsanity continue?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.49,1:21:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这将持续多久\NI don't know how long it's gonna last,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.59,1:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在，我不在乎\NBut right now, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.96,1:21:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪底角尝试三分\NLin out of the corner for 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.06,1:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,球进了！\NCount 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.80,1:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人说预料到这一切，那是在瞎说\NAnyone who said they saw this coming is lying!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.80,1:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他能做到的远不止于人们以为的那样\NThere's a lot more that he can do
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他的信心已经今非昔比\NThan anybody knew, and it comes down to confidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.44,1:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪突破\NJeremy on the drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.54,1:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,2+1打成\NAnd-1 for jeremy lin!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.54,1:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,打进还造成犯规\NHe got the bang and the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.91,1:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他有自己的招牌\NHe's got that swagger.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.81,1:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在很有范儿\NHe has that "it" right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.11,1:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这超越了体育的范畴\NThis transcends sports. It really does.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.75,1:22:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在当今体育界最美妙的故事里大放光芒\NHe has shined and evolved into {\i1}the{\i} best story in sports today.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.49,1:22:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.66,1:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在后场施加压力\NPressure in the backcourt.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.99,1:22:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪抢断，直捣黄龙\NOh, and lin the steal! To the basket!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.27,1:22:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,林书豪面对德克·诺维茨基的防守\NLin, over dirk.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.47,1:22:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,噢噢噢！\NOhh!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.51,1:22:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太精彩了\NHow good is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.24,1:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想去享受比赛\NI'm just out there having fun
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.55,1:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,打好球\NAnd playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.85,1:22:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会有表现不好的时候\NI can have bad games, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.18,1:22:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许会不喜欢我，会嘘我\NThey may not like me, or they may boo me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.99,1:22:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但生命中有很多事情远比篮球重要\NThere's a lot more important things in life than just basketball.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.55,1:22:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.29,1:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟篮球只是一场游戏\N'cause at the end of the day, basketball's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.23,1:22:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这场秀还在继续\NThe show continues on broadway.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.80,1:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个故事有很多亮点\NIt's a story with many spokes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.57,1:22:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,常春藤，美籍亚裔运动员\NAn ivy leaguer, asian-american athlete,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.94,1:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从替补席横空出世\NGuy off the end of the bench.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.77,1:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为所有没有得到机会的人代言\NSpeaks for everyone who didn't get their chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.17,1:23:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只是短短的几周，在纽约城\NIt's only a couple of weeks, but in new york city,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.61,1:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在篮球这一大舞台上\NAnd on basketball's big stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.78,1:23:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经把故事带出了篮球这个公园\NThis guy has hit it out of the park.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.25,1:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在我身上发生的故事\NWhat happened to me, the story that happened to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.08,1:23:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是说，我早就知道\NI mean, it wasn't like I knew
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.25,1:23:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我能从替补席上来完成那些事情\NI could just come off the bench and do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.22,1:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\NI really didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.39,1:23:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己有这个水平\NUm, I thought I could play at this level,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.89,1:23:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己可以成为好的球员\NAnd I thought I could be a good player,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.26,1:23:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没想到会发生这一系列事情\NBut I didn't feel like that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.16,1:23:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有些球场上的经历\NAnd some of those experiences out there when I was on the court,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.96,1:23:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.97,1:23:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己是被别的力量控制着\NI felt like I was being controlled by something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.14,1:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有些完全超出肉体\NI felt like I was having an out-of-body experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.77,1:23:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我完成的一些得分\NSome of the plays that I made,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.87,1:23:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的一些胜利\NSome of the wins that we had,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.64,1:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真的超出了这个世界\NWere just so out of this world
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.11,1:23:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我时常还要掐一下自己\NThat I still have to pinch myself
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.95,1:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才能相信这是真的\NTo really believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.35,1:23:51.98,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}职业生涯前9场首发比赛中{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.15,1:23:55.00,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}场均9.9次助攻，2.2次抢断{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.75,1:23:59.92,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}25.0分{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.53,1:24:08.53,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在NBA 65年的历史中\N这个记录前无古人{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.53,1:24:19.53,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他创纪录式的表现过后\N在休赛期成为自由球员{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.53,1:24:27.53,注解3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他只收到休斯顿火箭队的报价\N并最终签下3年2500万美元的合同{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.53,1:24:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}随着林书豪翻开新的篇章{\i}\N{\i1}As jeremy ends one chapter and begins another,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.40,1:24:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}前面的路将不断地考验他的毅力{\i}\N{\i1}The road ahead will continue to test his perseverance.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.18,1:24:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他的信念将永远指引他{\i}\N{\i1}But his faith will forever guide him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.95,1:24:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去年我学会了\NThe thing I had to learn last year
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.15,1:24:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的计划并不是\NIs a perfect plan doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.52,1:25:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的事情都如你所愿\NThat it ends up the way you want it to end up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.49,1:25:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你之前问我，什么是完美的计划\NIn the past, if you asked me what's a perfect plan,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.76,1:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能会答，“心想事成”\NI'd be like, "I get what I want,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.96,1:25:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“打好球，实现梦想”\NI get my dream, I play well."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.03,1:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我有新的看法\NNow I have a different perspective
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.90,1:25:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,关于什么才是完美的计划\NOn what a perfect plan is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.84,1:25:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你一直赢，你不会成长\NYou don't get better if you win all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.14,1:25:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只有失败才会让你成长\NYou know, you get better when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.94,1:25:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,失败让你提高\NYou improve when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.31,1:25:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,失败让你更加反思自我\NYou look at yourself more when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.21,1:25:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你我都学到很多\NSo if you learn a lot or if I learn a lot,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.85,1:25:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有很好的成长\NIf I grow a lot,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.32,1:25:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我随着时间流逝变成更好的人\NIf I become a better person through tough times,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.65,1:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是神的完美计划的一部分\NThat's part of his perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.09,1:25:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,才是神的完美旨意的一部分\NThat's part of his perfect will.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.84,1:25:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我感到缺乏安全感\NWhen I was going through all my insecurities
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.04,1:25:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,失去信心\NAnd uncertainty and lack of confidence,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.11,1:25:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我分散了对神的专注\NI was losing focus on god.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.85,1:25:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我把注意力放到别的事情上了\NI was focusing on all these other things,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.42,1:26:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比如我的工作和别人的想法\NLike my job and what other people thought of me
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.09,1:26:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以及各种对我的报道\NAnd what the reporters were writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.12,1:26:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但随着时间流逝，我会反思自己\NYou know, over time, I was able to check myself
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.83,1:26:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,找回我对神的专注\NAnd kind of get my focus back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.26,1:26:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得神对我做了一些超自然的事情\NAnd I think god did something supernatural in me,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.23,1:26:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一些我无法以一己之力完成的事情\NSomething that I couldn't do on my own,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.07,1:26:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有些我也许永远无法复制\NSomething that I may never be able to recreate.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.27,1:26:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在那件事上\NSo I think, in that instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.91,1:26:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是学着去奋斗\NI was just learning to fight
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.48,1:26:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去为了神而生活和打球\NTo constantly live and play for god.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.51,1:26:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我做到这些，我就能完成看似不可能的事情\NAnd when I do that, I'll be able to walk on water.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.21,1:27:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上面全是《狮子王》的角色\NIt's all about {\i1}lion king.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.91,1:27:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有娜娜\NWe have nala right here,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.53,1:27:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有小辛巴，丁满和彭彭\NBaby simba, timon and pumbaa.
